<h2>Tuesday, October 28 / Martes 28 de Octubre</h2>

<p>Today we went with our parents to the beach. We went to Tecoman, a town about 30 minutes from Colima city. The ocean here is rough so we didn’t swim. The food was phenomenal and we had a great time. That evening we went to have dinner to Roberto and Flor’s home.</p>

<p>Hoy nos fuimos con los papás de Héctor y la mamá de Karla a comer a la playa, al Crab en Tecomán. Como el mar ahí es picado, no nos metimos a nadar, pero nos la pasamos muy bien. En la noche nos fuimos a cenar a casa de Roberto y Flor.</p>

