INSERT INTO blogs VALUES(4,'2014-lake-erie','Lake Erie','2014-11-18 02:11:25.901565','2014-11-18 02:11:25.901565','<p>We spend Labor day weekend with our friends Jerry and Marti at their cottage in Lake Erie. / El fin de semana de <i>Labor Day</i> nos la pasamos en la casa junto al lago de nuestros amigos Jerry y Marti.</p>

<h2>Saturday</h2>
<p>Saturday morning we went to see the lake which is a 5-minute walk from the cottage. Although Lake Erie is the "smallest" of the Great Lakes it is still magnificent. / El sabado a primera hora fuimos a ver el lago que esta a 5 minutos caminando desde la casa, a pesar de que el Lago Erie es el mas "pequeño" de los Grandes Lagos, no deja de ser impresionante.</p>
<img alt="" src="https://s3-us-west-2.amazonaws.com/hectorykarla/2014/erie01_thumb.jpg" />
<img alt="" src="https://s3-us-west-2.amazonaws.com/hectorykarla/2014/erie02_thumb.jpg" />
<img alt="" src="https://s3-us-west-2.amazonaws.com/hectorykarla/2014/erie03_thumb.jpg" />

<p>After lunch we went to Presque Isle and paddled for a few hours on the lagoon. / Despues de lonchar fuimos a un parque estatal llamado Presque Isle que es una pequeña peninsula. Ahi nos las pasamos varias horas en nuestros kayaks en los canales dentro de la peninsula.</p>
<img alt="" src="https://s3-us-west-2.amazonaws.com/hectorykarla/2014/erie04_thumb.jpg" />
<img alt="" src="https://s3-us-west-2.amazonaws.com/hectorykarla/2014/erie05_thumb.jpg" />
<img alt="" src="https://s3-us-west-2.amazonaws.com/hectorykarla/2014/erie06_thumb.jpg" />

<p>In the afternoon Jerry grilled a pork loin and we had a lovely dinner. / En la tarde Jerry aso un lomo de puerco para la cena.</p>
<img alt="" src="https://s3-us-west-2.amazonaws.com/hectorykarla/2014/erie07_thumb.jpg" />
<img alt="" src="https://s3-us-west-2.amazonaws.com/hectorykarla/2014/erie08_thumb.jpg" />
<img alt="" src="https://s3-us-west-2.amazonaws.com/hectorykarla/2014/erie09_thumb.jpg" />

<p>Later that day we went back to the lake to enjoy the sunset. / Al atardecer regresamos al lago para disfrutar la vista con la puesta del sol.</p>
<img alt="" src="https://s3-us-west-2.amazonaws.com/hectorykarla/2014/erie10_thumb.jpg" />
<img alt="" src="https://s3-us-west-2.amazonaws.com/hectorykarla/2014/erie11_thumb.jpg" />
<img alt="" src="https://s3-us-west-2.amazonaws.com/hectorykarla/2014/erie12_thumb.jpg" />
<img alt="" src="https://s3-us-west-2.amazonaws.com/hectorykarla/2014/erie13_thumb.jpg" />

<h2>Sunday</h2>
<p>On Sunday we went to Dobbins Landing. We visited an art gallery, had lunch, and took a tour of the Peacemaker, of a 150-feet long sailboat anchored here for a few days. / El domingo fuimos al muelle, visitamos una galeria de arte, lonchamos, y entramos a ver un velero gigante llamado "Peacemaker".</p>
<img alt="" src="https://s3-us-west-2.amazonaws.com/hectorykarla/2014/erie14_thumb.jpg" />
<img alt="" src="https://s3-us-west-2.amazonaws.com/hectorykarla/2014/erie15_thumb.jpg" />
<img alt="" src="https://s3-us-west-2.amazonaws.com/hectorykarla/2014/erie16_thumb.jpg" />
<img alt="" src="https://s3-us-west-2.amazonaws.com/hectorykarla/2014/erie17_thumb.jpg" />
<img alt="" src="https://s3-us-west-2.amazonaws.com/hectorykarla/2014/erie18_thumb.jpg" />
<img alt="" src="https://s3-us-west-2.amazonaws.com/hectorykarla/2014/erie19_thumb.jpg" />
<img alt="" src="https://s3-us-west-2.amazonaws.com/hectorykarla/2014/erie20_thumb.jpg" />

<h2>Monday</h2>
<p>Monday we kayaked on Lake Erie but didn''t unfortunately we didn''t take pictures of this. Then we had lunch at the Avonia Tavern and headed back home. / El lunes tempranito fuimos con nuestros kayaks al lago, pero de eso no tenemos fotos. Despues lonchamos y nos venimos de regreso a casa.</p>
','https://s3-us-west-2.amazonaws.com/hectorykarla/2014/erie13_thumb.jpg','2014-08-29',2014,'Lake Erie','file-2014-lake-erie');
