INSERT INTO blogs VALUES(6,'2014-pittsburgh','Pittsburgh','2014-11-18 02:11:25.942964','2014-11-18 02:11:25.942964','<p>On Sunday we decided to take a one-day trip to Pittsburgh. / El domingo nos fuimos de ida y vuela a Pittsburgh. </p>

<h2>The Strip District</h2>
<p>Our first stop was the Strip District, where we had authentic mexican tacos for lunch. After that we walked around the shops, and got a few things here and there. / Lo primero que hicimos al llegar fue ir al Strip District por unos buenos taquitos mexicanos, y luego nos pusimos a pasear por las tiendas y mercaditos que estan alrededor. </p>
<img alt="" src="https://s3-us-west-2.amazonaws.com/hectorykarla/2014/pittsburgh01_thumb.jpg" />
