INSERT INTO blogs VALUES(7,'2014-prince-gallitzin','Prince Gallitzin','2014-11-18 02:11:25.998818','2014-11-18 02:11:25.998818','<p>This weekend we went camping to Prince Gallitzin. / Este fin de semana nos fuimos a acampar a un parque estatal llamado Prince Gallitzin.</p>

<h3>Friday, July 25th</h3>
<p>We camp rather primitive, we kill our own cattle and eat it on the spot. Just kidding, we bought these beautiful steaks at Wegman''s and grilled them on the fire for dinner. We then opened the marshmallows and a chocolate bar and warmed up by the fire. / Como pueden observar acampamos muy rustico y comemos pobremente en nuestras acampadas :)</p>
<img alt="" src="https://s3-us-west-2.amazonaws.com/hectorykarla/2014/princegallitzin01_thumb.jpg" />

<h3>Saturday, July 26th</h3>
<p>We started the day slow / El sabado lo empezamos tranquilitos descansando.</p>
<img alt="" src="https://s3-us-west-2.amazonaws.com/hectorykarla/2014/princegallitzin02_thumb.jpg" />

<p>Early in the afternoon Dan, Mac, and Hector went orienteering. Dan lead the way with the compass and Hector and Mac followed along. We did half of the intermediate loop without getting lost! but we had to cut it short because Mac was starting to look too tired. / En la tarde Dan, Mac y Hector se fueron de excursion con una brujula y un mapa por alguas partes del parque; logramos hacer la mitad del recorrido sin perdernos pero tuvimos que regresarnos cuando vimos que el pobre Mac estaba muy cansado. </p>
<img alt="" src="https://s3-us-west-2.amazonaws.com/hectorykarla/2014/princegallitzin03_thumb.jpg" />
<img alt="" src="https://s3-us-west-2.amazonaws.com/hectorykarla/2014/princegallitzin04_thumb.jpg" />
<img alt="" src="https://s3-us-west-2.amazonaws.com/hectorykarla/2014/princegallitzin05_thumb.jpg" />
<img alt="" src="https://s3-us-west-2.amazonaws.com/hectorykarla/2014/princegallitzin06_thumb.jpg" />
<img alt="" src="https://s3-us-west-2.amazonaws.com/hectorykarla/2014/princegallitzin07_thumb.jpg" />
<img alt="" src="https://s3-us-west-2.amazonaws.com/hectorykarla/2014/princegallitzin08_thumb.jpg" />
<img alt="" src="https://s3-us-west-2.amazonaws.com/hectorykarla/2014/princegallitzin09_thumb.jpg" />
<img alt="" src="https://s3-us-west-2.amazonaws.com/hectorykarla/2014/princegallitzin10_thumb.jpg" />
<img alt="" src="https://s3-us-west-2.amazonaws.com/hectorykarla/2014/princegallitzin11_thumb.jpg" />

<p>Back to our campsite, relaxing for a little bit. / De regreso en el campamento, todos descansando. </p>
<img alt="" src="https://s3-us-west-2.amazonaws.com/hectorykarla/2014/princegallitzin12_thumb.jpg" />
<img alt="" src="https://s3-us-west-2.amazonaws.com/hectorykarla/2014/princegallitzin13_thumb.jpg" />
<img alt="" src="https://s3-us-west-2.amazonaws.com/hectorykarla/2014/princegallitzin14_thumb.jpg" />
<img alt="" src="https://s3-us-west-2.amazonaws.com/hectorykarla/2014/princegallitzin15_thumb.jpg" />

<p>At night we cooked pasta for dinner. We started a fire but had to run into our tents because it started raining. After a little while we noticed that our fire was still going and that the rain had stopped so we went back to the fire ring and enjoyed the rest of the night without rain. / Para cenar cocinamos una pasta con vegetales asados en el azador. Despues de la cena nos cayo una lluvia y nos tuvimos que meter a nuestras tiendas de acampar, pero al poco rato se fue la lluvia y nos regresamos a nuestra fogata a disfrutar de la noche. </p>
<img alt="" src="https://s3-us-west-2.amazonaws.com/hectorykarla/2014/princegallitzin17_thumb.jpg" />
<img alt="" src="https://s3-us-west-2.amazonaws.com/hectorykarla/2014/princegallitzin18_thumb.jpg" />
<img alt="" src="https://s3-us-west-2.amazonaws.com/hectorykarla/2014/princegallitzin19_thumb.jpg" />
