<img alt="" src="https://s3-us-west-2.amazonaws.com/hectorykarla/2014/princegallitzin24_thumb.jpg" />

<h3>Sunday, July 27th</h3>
<p>Karla, Mac, and Hector went for a quick hike by the lake on one of the trails. / Karla, Mac y Hector se fueron a caminar en uno de los caminitos que bordean el lago. </p>
<img alt="" src="https://s3-us-west-2.amazonaws.com/hectorykarla/2014/princegallitzin25_thumb.jpg" />
<img alt="" src="https://s3-us-west-2.amazonaws.com/hectorykarla/2014/princegallitzin26_thumb.jpg" />
