<img alt="" src="https://s3-us-west-2.amazonaws.com/hectorykarla/2014/princegallitzin32_thumb.jpg" />

<p>Around noon, we packed our stuff and drove to the lake for a picnic. / Al medio dia recogimos nuestro campamento y nos fuimos de picnic a la orilla del lago. </p>
