<img alt="" src="https://s3-us-west-2.amazonaws.com/hectorykarla/2014/wingfest08_thumb.jpg" />

<p>I put somebody else''s sunglasses in front of the camera to take this picture, hence the rose/purple hint to it, no Instagram was used :) / El color rosado de esta foto del atardecer es porque puse los lentes obscuros de uno de los que estaba con nosotros en frente de la camara. </p>
<img alt="" src="https://s3-us-west-2.amazonaws.com/hectorykarla/2014/wingfest09_thumb.jpg" />

<p>Neither special effects nor somebody else''s glasses were used for this photo. The sky was just beautiful on our way out of the festival. / En esta foto no hice nada especial, asi es como se veia el cielo cuando nos regresamos del festival. </p>
<img alt="" src="https://s3-us-west-2.amazonaws.com/hectorykarla/2014/wingfest10_thumb.jpg" />

<p>After Wing Fest we went to hear Eric Farmer, Josh Troup, and Eric Burkhart at the Tavern./ Despues del festival fuimos a ver tocar a unos de nuesros amigos al restaurant The Tavern.</p>
<img alt="" src="https://s3-us-west-2.amazonaws.com/hectorykarla/2014/wingfest11_thumb.jpg" />
