<h4>Lunch at Toro Salao</h4>
<img alt="" src="https://s3-us-west-2.amazonaws.com/hectorykarla/2014/puertorico91_thumb.jpg" />
<img alt="" src="https://s3-us-west-2.amazonaws.com/hectorykarla/2014/puertorico92_thumb.jpg" />

<h4>Last dinner</h4>
<p>For our last dinner we stopped at Bebos again. Hector had the special of the day <i>mondongo</i> and Karla had <i>asopao</i>. Eating light before traveling is for the weak :) / <span class="spanish">Para nuestra ultima cena en San Juan regresamos a Bebos y pedimos el especial del dia (mondongo) y un asopao. Eso de comer ligero antes de un viaje es para los viejitos :) </span></p>
<img alt="" src="https://s3-us-west-2.amazonaws.com/hectorykarla/2014/puertorico93_thumb.jpg" />

<h3>May 21st</h3>
<p>We flew back to State College. / <span class="spanish">Volamos de regreso a State College.</span></p>
