INSERT INTO blogs VALUES(14,'2014-philadelphia','Philadelphia','2014-11-18 02:11:26.162042','2014-11-18 02:11:26.162042','<p>We arrived Friday night to Philadelphia and walked up to a small bar a block from our hotel and had a lot of fun chatting with the bartender and a few strangers, listening to music, drinking, and eating. / <span style="color: rgb(51, 153, 102);">Llegamos a Filadelfia el viernes por la noche y fuimos a un barecito que estaba a unas cuadras de nuestro hotel. Nos la pasamos a todo dar platicando con el cantinero y tomandonos una chelitas.</span></p>
<p><img alt="" src="https://s3-us-west-2.amazonaws.com/hectorykarla/2014/philadelphia01_thumb.jpg" /></p>
<h2>Saturday</h2>
<p>Saturday we went walking around town. Our hotel was only a couple of blocks from City Hall and a few more from Reading Terminal Market where we had breakfast. / <span style="color: rgb(51, 153, 102);">El sabado nos la pasamos caminando por toda la ciudad. Empezamos de nuestro hotel hasta el palacio de gobierno y de ahi a un mercado famoso donde desayunamos.</span>&nbsp;</p>
<p><img alt="" src="https://s3-us-west-2.amazonaws.com/hectorykarla/2014/philadelphia02_thumb.jpg" /> <img alt="" src="https://s3-us-west-2.amazonaws.com/hectorykarla/2014/philadelphia03_thumb.jpg" /> <img alt="" src="https://s3-us-west-2.amazonaws.com/hectorykarla/2014/philadelphia04_thumb.jpg" /> <img alt="" src="https://s3-us-west-2.amazonaws.com/hectorykarla/2014/philadelphia05_thumb.jpg" /></p>
<p>From the market we went to Chinatown. / <span style="color: rgb(51, 153, 102);">De ahi nos fuimos al barrio chino.&nbsp;</span></p>
<p><img alt="" src="https://s3-us-west-2.amazonaws.com/hectorykarla/2014/philadelphia06_thumb.jpg" /></p>
<p>..and from there to the Independence National Park. We didn''t enter to any of the historical attractions, we just walked around, chilled out on the grass, took pictures, and enjoyed the beautiful weather. / <span style="color: rgb(51, 153, 102);">...y de ahi nos fuimos al parque nacional de la independencia donde hay muchos edificios historicos, pero no entramos a ninguno de ellos, en su lugar nos la pasamos caminando alrededor y disfrutando el dia.</span>&nbsp;</p>
<p><img alt="" src="https://s3-us-west-2.amazonaws.com/hectorykarla/2014/philadelphia07_thumb.jpg" /> <img alt="" src="https://s3-us-west-2.amazonaws.com/hectorykarla/2014/philadelphia08_thumb.jpg" /> <img alt="" src="https://s3-us-west-2.amazonaws.com/hectorykarla/2014/philadelphia09_thumb.jpg" /> <img alt="" src="https://s3-us-west-2.amazonaws.com/hectorykarla/2014/philadelphia10_thumb.jpg" /> <img alt="" src="https://s3-us-west-2.amazonaws.com/hectorykarla/2014/philadelphia11_thumb.jpg" /> <img alt="" src="https://s3-us-west-2.amazonaws.com/hectorykarla/2014/philadelphia12_thumb.jpg" /></p>
<p>We kept walking until we reached Penn''s Landing and saw a few of the boats docked in there. There were a couple of very large sail boats that were 100+ years old plus a submarine. / <span style="color: rgb(51, 153, 102);">Seguimos caminando hasta llegar al rio donde nos toco ver un par de veleros gigantes y un submarino.</span></p>
<p><img alt="" src="https://s3-us-west-2.amazonaws.com/hectorykarla/2014/philadelphia13_thumb.jpg" /> <img alt="" src="https://s3-us-west-2.amazonaws.com/hectorykarla/2014/philadelphia14_thumb.jpg" /></p>
<p>To have lunch we walked to South Street. After that we walked into a flea market and some of the nearby neighborhoods. The architecture in this part of the town is beautiful. / <span style="color: rgb(51, 153, 102);">Para lonchar nos fuimos a un barrio que estaba por ahi. De ahi le echamos un vistazo al mercado de pulgas y seguimos caminando por los vecindarios de esta area que son preciosos con una arquitectura antig&uuml;a muy bella.</span> &nbsp;</p>
<p><img alt="" src="https://s3-us-west-2.amazonaws.com/hectorykarla/2014/philadelphia15_thumb.jpg" /> <img alt="" src="https://s3-us-west-2.amazonaws.com/hectorykarla/2014/philadelphia16_thumb.jpg" /> <img alt="" src="https://s3-us-west-2.amazonaws.com/hectorykarla/2014/philadelphia17_thumb.jpg" /> <img alt="" src="https://s3-us-west-2.amazonaws.com/hectorykarla/2014/philadelphia18_thumb.jpg" /> <img alt="" src="https://s3-us-west-2.amazonaws.com/hectorykarla/2014/philadelphia19_thumb.jpg" /> <img alt="" src="https://s3-us-west-2.amazonaws.com/hectorykarla/2014/philadelphia20_thumb.jpg" /> <img alt="" src="https://s3-us-west-2.amazonaws.com/hectorykarla/2014/philadelphia21_thumb.jpg" /> <img alt="" src="https://s3-us-west-2.amazonaws.com/hectorykarla/2014/philadelphia22_thumb.jpg" /></p>
<p>After walking for a while we took the bus back to the hotel but we ended up stopping at City Hall to take a few more pictures. / <span style="color: rgb(51, 153, 102);">Despues de caminar un buen rato tomamo el camion de regreso al hotel y paramos de nuevo en el palacio de gobierno para tomarle mas fotos.</span>&nbsp;</p>
<p><img alt="" src="https://s3-us-west-2.amazonaws.com/hectorykarla/2014/philadelphia23_thumb.jpg" /> <img alt="" src="https://s3-us-west-2.amazonaws.com/hectorykarla/2014/philadelphia24_thumb.jpg" /> <img alt="" src="https://s3-us-west-2.amazonaws.com/hectorykarla/2014/philadelphia25_thumb.jpg" /></p>
<p>&nbsp;</p>
<p>At night, we ended up going out for dinner to an italian restaurant. / <span style="color: rgb(51, 153, 102);">En la noche nos fuimos a cenar a un resturant italiano.</span></p>
<p><img alt="" src="https://s3-us-west-2.amazonaws.com/hectorykarla/2014/philadelphia26_thumb.jpg" /></p>
<h2>Sunday</h2>
<p>We went back to the market for dinner, and after that we walked around downtown stopping at some of the stores and shopping areas to browse around. / <span style="color: rgb(51, 153, 102);">El domingo fuimos a desayunar al mercado ota vez y de ahi seguimos caminando por otras partes de la ciudad, entrando a la tiendas y divagando sin ningun plan.&nbsp;</span></p>
<p><img alt="" src="https://s3-us-west-2.amazonaws.com/hectorykarla/2014/philadelphia27_thumb.jpg" /> <img alt="" src="https://s3-us-west-2.amazonaws.com/hectorykarla/2014/philadelphia28_thumb.jpg" /> <img alt="" src="https://s3-us-west-2.amazonaws.com/hectorykarla/2014/philadelphia29_thumb.jpg" /></p>','https://s3-us-west-2.amazonaws.com/hectorykarla/2014/philadelphia22_thumb.jpg','2014-04-17',2014,'Philadelphia 2014','4c746f5c-6941-4e40-869e-c23f40523f49');
