INSERT INTO blogs VALUES(16,'2014-mount-nittany','Mount Nittany','2014-11-18 02:11:26.222975','2014-11-18 02:11:26.222975','<p>Today I went hiking to Mount Nittany. I''ve done this many times before, in all sorts of weather conditions (including covered with snow.) But today was the first time where I am the first one that walks on the snow in the trails. After about a mile in the blue trail there were no footsteps in front of me anymore. Breaking throught the snow and ice the rest of the way was much more tiresome that I thought but I had the entire mountain to myself. Beautiful! / <span style="color: rgb(51, 153, 102);">Hoy me fui de excursion a Mount Nittany como lo he hecho muchas veces, a pesar de que no es la primera vez que lo camino con nieve, hoy me toco ser el primero en caminar en la nieve y fue bastante pesado hacer camino la mayor parte. Eso si, tenia la monta&ntilde;a para mi solito y el clima esta precioso.</span></p>
<h3>Ready to hike</h3>
<p><img alt="" src="https://s3-us-west-2.amazonaws.com/hectorykarla/2013/mtnittany01_thumb.jpg" /></p>
<p>&nbsp;</p>
<h3>The snow has been packed by many hiker before me /<span style="color: rgb(51, 153, 102);"> Se nota como mucha gente camino por aqui</span></h3>
