INSERT INTO blogs VALUES(21,'2013-christmas','Christmas','2014-11-18 02:11:26.418036','2014-12-01 04:20:52.648175','<h2>Christmas Eve / Nochebuena</h2>
<p>We started celebrating Christmas on Christmas Eve by having a nice charcuterie and cheese plate in our &quot;little cabin&quot; downstairs by the wood stove. / <span style="color: rgb(51, 153, 102);">El 24 la pasamos en la casa y empezamos con una rica tablita de queso, pan y vino en nuestra &quot;caba&ntilde;a&quot; en el piso de abajo junto a la estufita de le&ntilde;a.</span></p>
<p><img alt="" src="https://s3-us-west-2.amazonaws.com/hectorykarla/2013/xmas17_thumb.jpg" /> <img alt="" src="https://s3-us-west-2.amazonaws.com/hectorykarla/2013/xmas16_thumb.jpg" />  <img alt="" src="https://s3-us-west-2.amazonaws.com/hectorykarla/2013/xmas15_thumb.jpg" />  <img alt="" src="https://s3-us-west-2.amazonaws.com/hectorykarla/2013/xmas14_thumb.jpg" /></p>
<p>Later on we cooked a delicious Moroocan Lamb for our entree. Initially we were going to have our dinner in our dinning room, but we decided to stay downstairs by the fire. / <span style="color: rgb(51, 153, 102);">Mas tarde cocinamos unas ricas costillitas de borrego al estilo de Moroco como nuestro plato principal. Originalmente ibamos a cenar en el comedor pero decidimos continuarla en el piso de abajo para seguir disfrutando de la estufita.</span></p>
<p><img alt="" src="https://s3-us-west-2.amazonaws.com/hectorykarla/2013/xmas13_thumb.jpg" />  <img alt="" src="https://s3-us-west-2.amazonaws.com/hectorykarla/2013/xmas12_thumb.jpg" />  <img alt="" src="https://s3-us-west-2.amazonaws.com/hectorykarla/2013/xmas11_thumb.jpg" /></p>
<p><img alt="" src="https://s3-us-west-2.amazonaws.com/hectorykarla/2013/xmas10_thumb.jpg" />  <img alt="" src="https://s3-us-west-2.amazonaws.com/hectorykarla/2013/xmas09_thumb.jpg" />  <img alt="" src="https://s3-us-west-2.amazonaws.com/hectorykarla/2013/xmas08_thumb.jpg" />  <img alt="" src="https://s3-us-west-2.amazonaws.com/hectorykarla/2013/xmas07_thumb.jpg" /></p>
<h2>On Christmas Day / El dia de navidad</h2>
<p>We started Christmas day on a good note by watching a movie and drinking mimosas! / <span style="color: rgb(51, 153, 102);">Empezamos el dia viendo una pelicula y echandonos una mimosas (jugo de naranja con vino tinto espumoso!)</span></p>
<p><img alt="" src="https://s3-us-west-2.amazonaws.com/hectorykarla/2013/xmas06_thumb.jpg" /></p>
<p>In the afternoon we went to Dan''s to have dinner with him, his mom, and Jihee and Junghwan. / <span style="color: rgb(51, 153, 102);">En la tarde fuimos a cenar con Dan y su mama y unos amigos.&nbsp;</span></p>
<p><img alt="" src="https://s3-us-west-2.amazonaws.com/hectorykarla/2013/xmas04_thumb.jpg" />  <img alt="" src="https://s3-us-west-2.amazonaws.com/hectorykarla/2013/xmas03_thumb.jpg" /></p>
<p>Santa really loves us! We received a suprise box of Chocolates from David and Nancy and a bottle of Tequila form Mike. / <span style="color: rgb(51, 153, 102);">Santa nos quiere mucho y nos llegaron unos ricos (y preciosos!) chocolates de Kansas City que nos mandaron nuestros amigos David y Nancy y una botella de tequila que nos regalo Mike (uno de mis compa&ntilde;eros de la oficina)</span>&nbsp;</p>
<p><img alt="" src="https://s3-us-west-2.amazonaws.com/hectorykarla/2013/xmas02_thumb.jpg" />  <img alt="" src="https://s3-us-west-2.amazonaws.com/hectorykarla/2013/xmas01_thumb.jpg" /></p>
<p>&nbsp;</p>','https://s3-us-west-2.amazonaws.com/hectorykarla/2013/xmas10_thumb.jpg','2013-12-24',2013,'Christmas 2013','4035ffbd-5a60-4bde-8298-926c0c111487');
