INSERT INTO blogs VALUES(25,'2012-christmas','Christmas','2014-11-18 02:11:26.522222','2014-12-01 04:23:29.436124','<h3>Going for the Christmas tree / <span style="color: rgb(51, 153, 102); ">Llendo por el arbolito</span></h3>
<p>Plenty of trees to chose from / <span style="color: rgb(51, 153, 102); ">Habian muchos arbolitos para escoger.</span></p>
<p><img alt="" src="https://s3-us-west-2.amazonaws.com/hectorykarla/2012/xmas01_thumb.jpg" /></p>
<p>Looks like we have a winner! /<span style="color: rgb(51, 153, 102); "> Este es el nuestro!</span></p>
<p><img alt="" src="https://s3-us-west-2.amazonaws.com/hectorykarla/2012/xmas02_thumb.jpg" /></p>
<p>...and it''s coming down! / <span style="color: rgb(51, 153, 102); ">va pa''abajo</span></p>
<p><img alt="" src="https://s3-us-west-2.amazonaws.com/hectorykarla/2012/xmas03_thumb.jpg" /></p>
<p>Oops!...I think we underestimated how big it will feel inside the house :) / <span style="color: rgb(51, 153, 102); ">Orale...se me hace que le calculamos mal, el arbolito salio mas grande de lo que creiamos!</span></p>
<p><img alt="" src="https://s3-us-west-2.amazonaws.com/hectorykarla/2012/xmas04_thumb.jpg" /></p>
<p>Even Santa looks small on this tree /<span style="color: rgb(51, 153, 102); "> Hasta Santa se ve chiquito :)</span></p>
<p><img alt="" src="https://s3-us-west-2.amazonaws.com/hectorykarla/2012/xmas05_thumb.jpg" /></p>
<p>All decorated / <span style="color: rgb(51, 153, 102); ">Ya todo decorado</span></p>
<p>&nbsp;<img alt="" src="https://s3-us-west-2.amazonaws.com/hectorykarla/2012/xmas06_thumb.jpg" /></p>
<h3>Almost Christmas</h3>
<p>The Friday before Christmas Summer had to have surgery (she did fine) and therefore we were homebound for a few days. We had a great weekend in our &quot;winter home&quot; (also knows as downstairs) enjoying the fire from the woodstove, reading, watching movies, and having dinners in the &quot;H&amp;K Bistro&quot; / <span style="color: rgb(51, 153, 102); ">El viernes antes de navidad tuvieron que operar a Summer, afortunadamente todo salio bien pero nos forzo a quedarnos en casa varios dias en lo que se recuparaba...y no creas que sufrimos much, al contrario, lo disfrutamos de lo lindo en nuestro sotano, con la chimenea, leyendo, viendo peliculas, y comiendo en nuestro restaurancito el &quot;H&amp;K bistro&quot;.&nbsp;</span></p>
<p><img alt="" src="https://s3-us-west-2.amazonaws.com/hectorykarla/2012/xmas07_thumb.jpg" /></p>
<p><img alt="" src="https://s3-us-west-2.amazonaws.com/hectorykarla/2012/xmas08_thumb.jpg" /> <img alt="" src="https://s3-us-west-2.amazonaws.com/hectorykarla/2012/xmas09_thumb.jpg" /></p>
<h3>Christmas Eve / <span style="color: rgb(51, 153, 102); ">Noche buena</span></h3>
<p>On Christmas Eve we went to pick up the leg of pork and marinated it. / <span style="color: rgb(51, 153, 102); ">El 24 fuimos por la famosa pierna de puerco y la marinamos.</span>&nbsp;</p>
<p><img alt="" src="https://s3-us-west-2.amazonaws.com/hectorykarla/2012/xmas10_thumb.jpg" /></p>
<p>...there was barely any snow on the ground by then. / <span style="color: rgb(51, 153, 102); ">Casi no habia nada de nieve para entonces</span></p>
<p><img alt="" src="https://s3-us-west-2.amazonaws.com/hectorykarla/2012/xmas11_thumb.jpg" /></p>
<p><img alt="" src="https://s3-us-west-2.amazonaws.com/hectorykarla/2012/xmas12_thumb.jpg" /> <img alt="" src="https://s3-us-west-2.amazonaws.com/hectorykarla/2012/xmas13_thumb.jpg" /></p>
<h3>Christmas Day / <span style="color: rgb(51, 153, 102); ">Navidad</span></h3>
<p>Santa knows we are nerds and left a few books, notepads, and a pencil sharpener under our tree. / <span style="color: rgb(51, 153, 102); ">Santa sabe que somos un par de nerd y nos &nbsp;dejo unos libros debajo del arbolito</span></p>
<p><img alt="" src="https://s3-us-west-2.amazonaws.com/hectorykarla/2012/xmas14_thumb.jpg" /></p>
<p>...and it looks like we are having a white Christmas! / <span style="color: rgb(51, 153, 102); ">Se me hace que si vamos a tener una blanca navidad despues de todo.</span></p>
<p><img alt="" src="https://s3-us-west-2.amazonaws.com/hectorykarla/2012/xmas15_thumb.jpg" /></p>
<p>To celebrate Christmas we organized a potluck which resulted in a feast as you can see in the picures! / <span style="color: rgb(51, 153, 102); ">Para celebrar organizamos un lunch que resulto ser toda una comidota!</span></p>
<p><img alt="" src="https://s3-us-west-2.amazonaws.com/hectorykarla/2012/xmas16_thumb.jpg" /> <img alt="" src="https://s3-us-west-2.amazonaws.com/hectorykarla/2012/xmas17_thumb.jpg" /> <img alt="" src="https://s3-us-west-2.amazonaws.com/hectorykarla/2012/xmas18_thumb.jpg" /> <img alt="" src="https://s3-us-west-2.amazonaws.com/hectorykarla/2012/xmas19_thumb.jpg" /> <img alt="" src="https://s3-us-west-2.amazonaws.com/hectorykarla/2012/xmas20_thumb.jpg" /> <img alt="" src="https://s3-us-west-2.amazonaws.com/hectorykarla/2012/xmas21_thumb.jpg" /> <img alt="" src="https://s3-us-west-2.amazonaws.com/hectorykarla/2012/xmas22_thumb.jpg" /> <img alt="" src="https://s3-us-west-2.amazonaws.com/hectorykarla/2012/xmas23_thumb.jpg" /> <img alt="" src="https://s3-us-west-2.amazonaws.com/hectorykarla/2012/xmas24_thumb.jpg" /> <img alt="" src="https://s3-us-west-2.amazonaws.com/hectorykarla/2012/xmas25_thumb.jpg" /> <img alt="" src="https://s3-us-west-2.amazonaws.com/hectorykarla/2012/xmas26_thumb.jpg" /> <img alt="" src="https://s3-us-west-2.amazonaws.com/hectorykarla/2012/xmas27_thumb.jpg" /> <img alt="" src="https://s3-us-west-2.amazonaws.com/hectorykarla/2012/xmas28_thumb.jpg" /> <img alt="" src="https://s3-us-west-2.amazonaws.com/hectorykarla/2012/xmas29_thumb.jpg" /> <img alt="" src="https://s3-us-west-2.amazonaws.com/hectorykarla/2012/xmas30_thumb.jpg" /> <img alt="" src="https://s3-us-west-2.amazonaws.com/hectorykarla/2012/xmas31_thumb.jpg" /> <img alt="" src="https://s3-us-west-2.amazonaws.com/hectorykarla/2012/xmas32_thumb.jpg" /> <img alt="" src="https://s3-us-west-2.amazonaws.com/hectorykarla/2012/xmas33_thumb.jpg" /> <img alt="" src="https://s3-us-west-2.amazonaws.com/hectorykarla/2012/xmas34_thumb.jpg" /> <img alt="" src="https://s3-us-west-2.amazonaws.com/hectorykarla/2012/xmas35_thumb.jpg" /> <img alt="" src="https://s3-us-west-2.amazonaws.com/hectorykarla/2012/xmas36_thumb.jpg" /> <img alt="" src="https://s3-us-west-2.amazonaws.com/hectorykarla/2012/xmas37_thumb.jpg" /></p>
<p>The whole gang (11 + 2) / <span style="color: rgb(51, 153, 102); ">Toda la bola</span></p>
<p><img alt="" src="https://s3-us-west-2.amazonaws.com/hectorykarla/2012/xmas38_thumb.jpg" /></p>
<p><img alt="" src="https://s3-us-west-2.amazonaws.com/hectorykarla/2012/xmas39_thumb.jpg" /> <img alt="" src="https://s3-us-west-2.amazonaws.com/hectorykarla/2012/xmas40_thumb.jpg" /> <img alt="" src="https://s3-us-west-2.amazonaws.com/hectorykarla/2012/xmas41_thumb.jpg" /> <img alt="" src="https://s3-us-west-2.amazonaws.com/hectorykarla/2012/xmas42_thumb.jpg" /> <img alt="" src="https://s3-us-west-2.amazonaws.com/hectorykarla/2012/xmas43_thumb.jpg" /> <img alt="" src="https://s3-us-west-2.amazonaws.com/hectorykarla/2012/xmas44_thumb.jpg" /></p>
<h3>The day after Christmas / <span style="color: rgb(51, 153, 102); ">El dia despues de navidad</span></h3>
<p>We got a few inches of snow overnight and the city looks beautiful. Karla and I took a walk around the neighborhood at night and it was georgeous. / <span style="color: rgb(51, 153, 102); ">Nos cayo una buena nevada en la madrugada y la ciudad se ve hermosa, tanto que hasta nos fuimos a dar un paseo caminando por el vecindario.</span></p>
<p><img alt="" src="https://s3-us-west-2.amazonaws.com/hectorykarla/2012/xmas45_thumb.jpg" /> <img alt="" src="https://s3-us-west-2.amazonaws.com/hectorykarla/2012/xmas46_thumb.jpg" /> <img alt="" src="https://s3-us-west-2.amazonaws.com/hectorykarla/2012/xmas47_thumb.jpg" /> <img alt="" src="https://s3-us-west-2.amazonaws.com/hectorykarla/2012/xmas48_thumb.jpg" /> <img alt="" src="https://s3-us-west-2.amazonaws.com/hectorykarla/2012/xmas49_thumb.jpg" /> <img alt="" src="https://s3-us-west-2.amazonaws.com/hectorykarla/2012/xmas50_thumb.jpg" /> <img alt="" src="https://s3-us-west-2.amazonaws.com/hectorykarla/2012/xmas51_thumb.jpg" /> <img alt="" src="https://s3-us-west-2.amazonaws.com/hectorykarla/2012/xmas52_thumb.jpg" /> <img alt="" src="https://s3-us-west-2.amazonaws.com/hectorykarla/2012/xmas53_thumb.jpg" /> <img alt="" src="https://s3-us-west-2.amazonaws.com/hectorykarla/2012/xmas54_thumb.jpg" /></p>
<p>A rare sight these days...sunshine! / <span style="color: rgb(51, 153, 102); ">Finalmente salio el sol!!!</span></p>
<p><img alt="" src="https://s3-us-west-2.amazonaws.com/hectorykarla/2012/xmas55_thumb.jpg" /></p>
