INSERT INTO blogs VALUES(47,'2011-black-moshannon','Black Moshannon','2014-11-18 02:11:27.077652','2014-12-01 04:31:34.289757','<p>Today (September 11th, 2011) we took our kayaks to Black Moshannon State Park. We camped on this park last year ([[[Black Moshannon 2010]]]) and we knew the scenery was beautiful. The water in this lake is black due to all the vegetation that lives at the bottom of the lake. You can learn more about this on their <a target="_blank" href="http://www.dcnr.state.pa.us/stateparks/parks/blackmoshannon.aspx">state park web site</a>.&nbsp;</p>
