INSERT INTO blogs VALUES(57,'2011-pittsburgh','Pittsburgh','2014-11-18 02:11:27.269549','2015-05-25 19:07:02.204476','<p>To take advantage that Karla was on Sprint Break we went to Pittsburgh to spend the day on Friday March 11th, 2011. Dan and Hyunny came with us and we had a great time &quot;in the big city&quot; :) / <span style="color: rgb(51, 153, 102); ">Para aprovechar que Karla estaba de vacaciones en la escuela el viernes nos dimos una escapadita a Pittsburgh, la segunda ciudad mas grande en el estado de Pennsylvania. Nuestros amigos Dan y Hyunny vinieron con nosotros y nos las pasamos a todo dar.</span></p>
<p>On our way there we missed our exit to take the main highway to Pittsburgh and ended up backing up through a few small roads that turned out with a great scenery as the snow has quite melted there. / <span style="color: rgb(51, 153, 102); ">De ida nos pasamos la salida en la que debimos de haber tomalos la autopista principal y nos animamos a tomar unas carreteras secundarias y nos toco una vista preciosa de la parte rural de Pennsylvania.&nbsp;</span></p>
<p><img alt="" src="https://s3-us-west-2.amazonaws.com/hectorykarla/2011/pittsburgh01_sm_thumb.jpg" />&nbsp;<img alt="" src="https://s3-us-west-2.amazonaws.com/hectorykarla/2011/pittsburgh03_sm_thumb.jpg" /><img alt="" src="https://s3-us-west-2.amazonaws.com/hectorykarla/2011/pittsburgh04_sm_thumb.jpg" />&nbsp;</p>
<p>After 2 1/2 hours of driving we made it to the tunnel into the city. / <span style="color: rgb(51, 153, 102); ">Y finalmente despues de 2 horas y media llegamos a Pittsburgh.</span></p>
<p><img alt="" src="https://s3-us-west-2.amazonaws.com/hectorykarla/2011/pittsburgh05_sm_thumb.jpg" /></p>
<p>The first thing we did when we got there was to drive to The Strip and have breakfast at Deluca''s. Dan and Hyunny had a gigantic waffle sundae and we had huevos rancheros. The huevos rancheros weren''t exactly what we were picturing but the chorizo was really good. / <span style="color: rgb(51, 153, 102); ">Lo primero que hicimos al llegar fue ir a un restaurant tipico a desayunar, nosotros pedimos unos huevos rancheros y Dan y Hyunny un &quot;sundae waffle&quot;. Los huevos rancheros no estuvieron muy mexicanos que digamos pero al menos el chorizo tenia buen sabor.</span></p>
<p><img alt="" src="https://s3-us-west-2.amazonaws.com/hectorykarla/2011/pittsburgh06_sm_thumb.jpg" />&nbsp;<img alt="" src="https://s3-us-west-2.amazonaws.com/hectorykarla/2011/pittsburgh07_sm_thumb.jpg" /><img alt="" src="https://s3-us-west-2.amazonaws.com/hectorykarla/2011/pittsburgh09_sm_thumb.jpg" />&nbsp;</p>
<p>After breakfast we spend the rest of the day shopping around the stores in the Strip and eating there along the way because after all we had a light breakfast as clearly shown in the previous pictures. / <span style="color: rgb(51, 153, 102); ">Despues del desayuno nos la pasamos de compras en un barrio muy pintoresco que se llama &quot;The Strip&quot;</span>&nbsp;</p>
<p><img alt="" src="https://s3-us-west-2.amazonaws.com/hectorykarla/2011/pittsburgh10_sm_thumb.jpg" /></p>
<p><img alt="" src="https://s3-us-west-2.amazonaws.com/hectorykarla/2011/pittsburgh11_sm_thumb.jpg" />&nbsp;<img alt="" src="https://s3-us-west-2.amazonaws.com/hectorykarla/2011/pittsburgh12_sm_thumb.jpg" />&nbsp;</p>
<p>At the italian market / <span style="color: rgb(51, 153, 102); ">En la tienda de quesos y jamones italianos.</span></p>
<p><img alt="" src="https://s3-us-west-2.amazonaws.com/hectorykarla/2011/pittsburgh14_sm_thumb.jpg" />&nbsp;<img alt="" src="https://s3-us-west-2.amazonaws.com/hectorykarla/2011/pittsburgh15_sm_thumb.jpg" /><img alt="" src="https://s3-us-west-2.amazonaws.com/hectorykarla/2011/pittsburgh16_sm_thumb.jpg" /></p>
<p>At the biscotti shop / <span style="color: rgb(51, 153, 102); ">En la tienda de biscottis.</span></p>
<p><img alt="" src="https://s3-us-west-2.amazonaws.com/hectorykarla/2011/pittsburgh17_sm_thumb.jpg" /><img alt="" src="https://s3-us-west-2.amazonaws.com/hectorykarla/2011/pittsburgh18_sm_thumb.jpg" /></p>
<p>At the (fancy) shop for spices / <span style="color: rgb(51, 153, 102); ">En una tienda muy fina de especies de cocina.</span></p>
<p><img alt="" src="https://s3-us-west-2.amazonaws.com/hectorykarla/2011/pittsburgh19_sm_thumb.jpg" />&nbsp;<img alt="" src="https://s3-us-west-2.amazonaws.com/hectorykarla/2011/pittsburgh35_sm_thumb.jpg" /></p>
<p>Around the strip / <span style="color: rgb(51, 153, 102); ">Caminando por el vecindario</span></p>
<p><img alt="" src="https://s3-us-west-2.amazonaws.com/hectorykarla/2011/pittsburgh20_sm_thumb.jpg" />&nbsp;<img alt="" src="https://s3-us-west-2.amazonaws.com/hectorykarla/2011/pittsburgh25_sm_thumb.jpg" /><img alt="" src="https://s3-us-west-2.amazonaws.com/hectorykarla/2011/pittsburgh26_sm_thumb.jpg" />&nbsp;<img alt="" src="https://s3-us-west-2.amazonaws.com/hectorykarla/2011/pittsburgh27_sm_thumb.jpg" /></p>
<p>I am guessing this coffee is caffeinated.&nbsp;</p>
<p><img alt="" src="https://s3-us-west-2.amazonaws.com/hectorykarla/2011/pittsburgh28_sm_thumb.jpg" /></p>
<p>Street tacos outside of Reyna Foods. / <span style="color: rgb(51, 153, 102); ">Tacos de carreton</span></p>
<p><img alt="" src="https://s3-us-west-2.amazonaws.com/hectorykarla/2011/pittsburgh29_sm_thumb.jpg" />&nbsp;<img alt="" src="https://s3-us-west-2.amazonaws.com/hectorykarla/2011/pittsburgh30_sm_thumb.jpg" /><img alt="" src="https://s3-us-west-2.amazonaws.com/hectorykarla/2011/pittsburgh31_sm_thumb.jpg" />&nbsp;<img alt="" src="https://s3-us-west-2.amazonaws.com/hectorykarla/2011/pittsburgh32_sm_thumb.jpg" />&nbsp;</p>
<p>At the fish market / <span style="color: rgb(51, 153, 102); ">En la pescaderia</span></p>
<p><img alt="" src="https://s3-us-west-2.amazonaws.com/hectorykarla/2011/pittsburgh36_sm_thumb.jpg" /></p>
<p>Around the strip.&nbsp;</p>
<p><img alt="" src="https://s3-us-west-2.amazonaws.com/hectorykarla/2011/pittsburgh37_sm_thumb.jpg" /><img alt="" src="https://s3-us-west-2.amazonaws.com/hectorykarla/2011/pittsburgh38_sm_thumb.jpg" /></p>
<p>Pattes at the Crested Duck charcuterie. / <span style="color: rgb(51, 153, 102); ">Una tienda de pates</span></p>
<p><img alt="" src="https://s3-us-west-2.amazonaws.com/hectorykarla/2011/pittsburgh39_sm_thumb.jpg" />&nbsp;</p>
<p>Flavored marshmallows including Guinness, Irish Coffee and Tequila. They were good. / <span style="color: rgb(51, 153, 102); ">Malvaviscos con sabores a tequila y cerveza.</span></p>
<p><img alt="" src="https://s3-us-west-2.amazonaws.com/hectorykarla/2011/pittsburgh40_sm_thumb.jpg" /></p>
<p>After a few hours of shopping we had to go back to the car to drop our groceries and be able to keep going...we were not going to let the heavy way of those bags slow us down, were we? &nbsp;</p>
<p><img alt="" src="https://s3-us-west-2.amazonaws.com/hectorykarla/2011/pittsburgh41_sm_thumb.jpg" /><img alt="" src="https://s3-us-west-2.amazonaws.com/hectorykarla/2011/pittsburgh42_sm_thumb.jpg" /><img alt="" src="https://s3-us-west-2.amazonaws.com/hectorykarla/2011/pittsburgh43_sm_thumb.jpg" /></p>
<p>Round two at the strip :)</p>
<p><img alt="" src="https://s3-us-west-2.amazonaws.com/hectorykarla/2011/pittsburgh44_sm_thumb.jpg" />&nbsp;<img alt="" src="https://s3-us-west-2.amazonaws.com/hectorykarla/2011/pittsburgh45_sm_thumb.jpg" /></p>
<p>After the strip we went out to Trader Joe''s and stopped at Abay, an ethiopian restaurant, for dinner before heading back home. / <span style="color: rgb(51, 153, 102); ">Para la cena fuimos a un restaurant etipioano.</span></p>
<p><img alt="" src="https://s3-us-west-2.amazonaws.com/hectorykarla/2011/pittsburgh46_sm_thumb.jpg" />&nbsp;<img alt="" src="https://s3-us-west-2.amazonaws.com/hectorykarla/2011/pittsburgh47_sm_thumb.jpg" /></p>','https://s3-us-west-2.amazonaws.com/hectorykarla/2011/pittsburgh41_sm_thumb.jpg','2011-03-13',2011,'Pittsburgh 2011','8cd5132a-22cf-431a-8177-4997e064a480');
INSERT INTO blogs VALUES(58,'2011-snow-march','Snow March','2014-11-18 02:11:27.289935','2015-05-25 19:08:27.670195','<p>To kick of &quot;Sprint Break&quot; we got between 9 and 11 inches of snow on March 6th! The biggest snowfall in a single day all this winter in State College. Woo-hoo!</p>
<h3>The view from our deck at night</h3>
<p><img alt="" src="https://s3-us-west-2.amazonaws.com/hectorykarla/2011/marchsnow01_sm_thumb.jpg" />&nbsp;&nbsp;<img alt="" src="https://s3-us-west-2.amazonaws.com/hectorykarla/2011/marchsnow03_sm_thumb.jpg" />&nbsp;&nbsp;</p>
<p><img alt="" src="https://s3-us-west-2.amazonaws.com/hectorykarla/2011/marchsnow05_sm_thumb.jpg" />&nbsp;&nbsp;</p>
<h3>Our front porch</h3>
<p><img alt="" src="https://s3-us-west-2.amazonaws.com/hectorykarla/2011/marchsnow07_sm_thumb.jpg" />&nbsp;&nbsp;<img alt="" src="https://s3-us-west-2.amazonaws.com/hectorykarla/2011/marchsnow09_sm_thumb.jpg" />&nbsp;</p>
<h3>The back yard</h3>
<p><img alt="" src="https://s3-us-west-2.amazonaws.com/hectorykarla/2011/marchsnow11_sm_thumb.jpg" />&nbsp;<img alt="" src="https://s3-us-west-2.amazonaws.com/hectorykarla/2011/marchsnow13_sm_thumb.jpg" />&nbsp;<img alt="" src="https://s3-us-west-2.amazonaws.com/hectorykarla/2011/marchsnow14_sm_thumb.jpg" />&nbsp;<img alt="" src="https://s3-us-west-2.amazonaws.com/hectorykarla/2011/marchsnow15_sm_thumb.jpg" />&nbsp;</p>
<h3>The next morning</h3>
