INSERT INTO blogs VALUES(62,'2010-black-moshannon','Black Moshannon','2014-11-18 02:11:27.392686','2015-05-25 20:18:17.649318','<p>This weekend (October 2nd and 3rd, 2010) we went camping to <a target="_blank" href="http://www.dcnr.state.pa.us/stateparks/parks/blackmoshannon.aspx">Black Moshannon State Park</a> with Dan and Hyunny. Even though it was a bit cold at night we had a great time talking, eating (a lot!), and hiking. / <span style="color: rgb(51, 153, 102); ">Este fin de semana nos fuimos a acampar con unos amigos a un parque que se llama</span>&nbsp;&nbsp;<a target="_blank" href="http://www.dcnr.state.pa.us/stateparks/parks/blackmoshannon.aspx">Black Moshannon State Park</a>&nbsp;<span style="color: rgb(51, 153, 102); ">y nos la pasamos a todo dar a pesar de que estuvo bastante frio en la madrugada.</span>&nbsp;</p>
<h2>Saturday</h2>
<p>As soon as we arrived to the park and setup the site Dan and Hyunni took care of lunch with some <strike>home made</strike>&nbsp;camp made bread and a stew with salmon and grains. Yummy...I am getting hungry again. / <span style="color: rgb(51, 153, 102); ">El sabado Dan y Hyunny se encargaron del lunch y aventaron una sopa con salmon y arroz ademas de un pan echo en la fogata!</span></p>
<p><img alt="" src="https://s3-us-west-2.amazonaws.com/hectorykarla/misc/pa020001_thumb.jpg" />&nbsp;<img alt="" src="https://s3-us-west-2.amazonaws.com/hectorykarla/misc/pa020004_thumb.jpg" /></p>
<p><img alt="" src="https://s3-us-west-2.amazonaws.com/hectorykarla/misc/pa020005_thumb.jpg" /></p>
<p><img alt="" src="https://s3-us-west-2.amazonaws.com/hectorykarla/misc/pa020010_thumb.jpg" />&nbsp;<img alt="" src="https://s3-us-west-2.amazonaws.com/hectorykarla/misc/pa020012_thumb.jpg" /></p>
<p>&nbsp;</p>
<p>After lunch we went for a hike around a small portion of the lake. Look at that view! / <span style="color: rgb(51, 153, 102); ">Despues del lunch nos fuimos a caminar alrededor del lago, echale un ojo a la vista que nos toco con las hojas cambiando de color en el oto&ntilde;o.&nbsp;</span></p>
<p><img alt="" src="https://s3-us-west-2.amazonaws.com/hectorykarla/misc/pa020016_thumb.jpg" />&nbsp;<img alt="" src="https://s3-us-west-2.amazonaws.com/hectorykarla/misc/pa020017_thumb.jpg" /></p>
<p><img alt="" src="https://s3-us-west-2.amazonaws.com/hectorykarla/misc/pa020018_thumb.jpg" />&nbsp;<img alt="" src="https://s3-us-west-2.amazonaws.com/hectorykarla/misc/pa020024_thumb.jpg" /></p>
<p><img alt="" src="https://s3-us-west-2.amazonaws.com/hectorykarla/misc/pa020030_thumb.jpg" /></p>
