<p><img alt="" src="https://s3-us-west-2.amazonaws.com/hectorykarla/misc/pa020035_thumb.jpg" />&nbsp;<img alt="" src="https://s3-us-west-2.amazonaws.com/hectorykarla/misc/pa020036_thumb.jpg" /></p>
<p><img alt="" src="https://s3-us-west-2.amazonaws.com/hectorykarla/misc/pa020039_thumb.jpg" />&nbsp;<img alt="" src="https://s3-us-west-2.amazonaws.com/hectorykarla/misc/pa020040_thumb.jpg" /></p>
<p><img alt="" src="https://s3-us-west-2.amazonaws.com/hectorykarla/misc/pa020041_thumb.jpg" />&nbsp;</p>
<p>&nbsp;</p>
<p>Back at the campsite...this is how grad students get their kicks :) / <span style="color: rgb(51, 153, 102); ">De regreso al campamento los estudiantes de doctorado le dieron un rato a la tarea -- a leer se ha dicho! :)&nbsp;</span></p>
<p><img alt="" src="https://s3-us-west-2.amazonaws.com/hectorykarla/misc/pa020044_thumb.jpg" /></p>
<p>&nbsp;</p>
<h2>Sunday</h2>
<p>Sunday we woke up late and after Dan and Hyunny left we went for a hike to another small trail on the park. / <span style="color: rgb(51, 153, 102); ">En domingo nos levantamos tarde y despues de que Dan y Hyunny se fueron Karla y yo nos fuimos a dar otra caminadita por el parque.&nbsp;</span></p>
<p><img alt="" src="https://s3-us-west-2.amazonaws.com/hectorykarla/misc/pa030045_thumb.jpg" /></p>
<p><img alt="" src="https://s3-us-west-2.amazonaws.com/hectorykarla/misc/pa030048_thumb.jpg" />&nbsp;<img alt="" src="https://s3-us-west-2.amazonaws.com/hectorykarla/misc/pa030049_thumb.jpg" /></p>
<p>Check out the cabins...we should start planning a trip here when we get some snow!&nbsp;</p>
<p><img alt="" src="https://s3-us-west-2.amazonaws.com/hectorykarla/misc/pa030051_thumb.jpg" />&nbsp;</p>
<p>&nbsp;</p>
<p>After a few wrong turns we finally found the famous Seneca trail that we''ve been meaning to take. The wait was worth it. Judge for yourself. / <span style="color: rgb(51, 153, 102); ">Despues de casi perdernos un par de veces finalmente encontramos la entrada al caminito que estabamos buscando -- y que bueno por que de veras que estuvo bonito.&nbsp;</span></p>
<p><img alt="" src="https://s3-us-west-2.amazonaws.com/hectorykarla/misc/pa030054_thumb.jpg" />&nbsp;<img alt="" src="https://s3-us-west-2.amazonaws.com/hectorykarla/misc/pa030056_thumb.jpg" /></p>
