<p><img alt="" src="https://s3-us-west-2.amazonaws.com/hectorykarla/misc/pa030091_thumb.jpg" /></p>
<p>&nbsp;</p>
<p>Karla was able to get a few good shots of the scenery around the park on the way back home. / <span style="color: rgb(51, 153, 102); ">Ya de regreso Karla tomo estas fotos de los alrededores para que se den un quemos de por donde andabamos.&nbsp;</span></p>
<p><img alt="" src="https://s3-us-west-2.amazonaws.com/hectorykarla/misc/pa030093_thumb.jpg" />&nbsp;<img alt="" src="https://s3-us-west-2.amazonaws.com/hectorykarla/misc/pa030096_thumb.jpg" /></p>
