INSERT INTO blogs VALUES(65,'2010-christmas','Christmas','2014-11-18 02:11:27.449565','2015-05-25 19:19:19.566909','<p>After a great Thanksgiving dinner with our friends (see [[[Thanksgiving 2010]]]) we started getting ready for Christmas! / <span style="color: rgb(51, 153, 102); ">Ya que pasaron los festejos del dia de accion de gracias nos empezamos a preparar para Navidad.</span></p>
<h2>Saturday November 27th</h2>
<p>After stacking two cords of wood on Friday, today we went to buy our Christmas tree. One of the advantages of living in the middle of Pennsylvania is that there are plenty several Christmas tree farms where you can go and cut your own tree. Today was very cold (in the low 30s with feel-like temperatures in the 20s) which made it even a more interesting adventure. / <span style="color: rgb(51, 153, 102); ">Despues de acomodar toda la le&ntilde;a el viernes hoy sabado nos fuimos a comprar nuestro arbolito de Navidad. Una de las ventajas de vivir en Pennsylvania es que hay varios lugares donde puedes ir a cortar tu propio arbolito y llevartelo fresquesito a tu casa asi que fuimos a uno de esos lugares a (pesar de que la temperatura estaba a 0 grados centigrados!) y escogimos el nuestro.</span></p>
<p><img alt="" src="https://s3-us-west-2.amazonaws.com/hectorykarla/2010/xmas01_sm_thumb.jpg" />&nbsp;<img alt="" src="https://s3-us-west-2.amazonaws.com/hectorykarla/2010/xmas02_sm_thumb.jpg" />&nbsp;</p>
<h2>Sunday November 28th</h2>
<p>Today we actually decorated our Christmas tree. It looks beautiful! / <span style="color: rgb(51, 153, 102); ">Hoy finalmente pusimos el arbolito en la casa y lo decoramos, a poco no se ve hermoso?</span></p>
<p>&nbsp;<img alt="" src="https://s3-us-west-2.amazonaws.com/hectorykarla/2010/pb280190_sm_thumb.jpg" /></p>
<p>&nbsp;and so does our wood burning stove&nbsp;/ <span style="color: rgb(51, 153, 102); ">una foto de nuestra &quot;chimenea&quot; que mas bien es un horno.</span></p>
<p><img alt="" src="https://s3-us-west-2.amazonaws.com/hectorykarla/2010/pb280184_sm_thumb.jpg" />&nbsp;</p>
<h2>Christmas Eve / Noche Buena</h2>
<p>Proof that Santa came to our house and left a few presents under the tree. / <span style="color: rgb(51, 153, 102); ">Santa Claus nos dio una visitadita y dejo unos unos regalitos porque nos portamos bien este a&ntilde;o.</span></p>
<p><img alt="" src="https://s3-us-west-2.amazonaws.com/hectorykarla/2010/xmas03_sm_thumb.jpg" />&nbsp;&nbsp;<img alt="" src="https://s3-us-west-2.amazonaws.com/hectorykarla/2010/xmas08_sm_thumb.jpg" /></p>
<p>&nbsp;</p>
<p>H&amp;K ready for party time / <span style="color: rgb(51, 153, 102); ">Hector y Karla ya listos para la pachanga.</span>&nbsp;</p>
<p><img alt="" src="https://s3-us-west-2.amazonaws.com/hectorykarla/2010/xmas04_sm_thumb.jpg" />&nbsp;<img alt="" src="https://s3-us-west-2.amazonaws.com/hectorykarla/2010/xmas05_sm_thumb.jpg" />&nbsp;</p>
<p>&nbsp;</p>
<p>Table is ready and food is almost there. / <span style="color: rgb(51, 153, 102); ">La mesa ya esta lista y la cena ya casi.</span></p>
<p><img alt="" src="https://s3-us-west-2.amazonaws.com/hectorykarla/2010/xmas06_sm_thumb.jpg" />&nbsp;<img alt="" src="https://s3-us-west-2.amazonaws.com/hectorykarla/2010/xmas07_sm_thumb.jpg" />&nbsp;&nbsp;</p>
<p>&nbsp;</p>
<p>Dinner is ready: pork shoulder and as they say on &quot;My Big Fat Greek Weeding&quot; for the vegetarians leg of lamb :) / <span style="color: rgb(51, 153, 102); ">La cena ya esta lista: lomo de puerco y como dicen en la pelicula &quot;Casarse es en Griego&quot; pierna de borrego para los vegetarianos.&nbsp;</span></p>
<p><img alt="" src="https://s3-us-west-2.amazonaws.com/hectorykarla/2010/xmas09_sm_thumb.jpg" />&nbsp;<img alt="" src="https://s3-us-west-2.amazonaws.com/hectorykarla/2010/xmas10_sm_thumb.jpg" /></p>
<p><img alt="" src="https://s3-us-west-2.amazonaws.com/hectorykarla/2010/xmas11_sm_thumb.jpg" />&nbsp;</p>
<p>&nbsp;</p>
<p>The gang / <span style="color: rgb(51, 153, 102); ">El grupo</span></p>
<p><img alt="" src="https://s3-us-west-2.amazonaws.com/hectorykarla/2010/xmas12_sm_thumb.jpg" /></p>
<p>&nbsp;</p>
<p>The mess after opening presents. We gave each other mostly cloths and for the PhD student a bookcase (quite proper) /&nbsp;<span style="color: rgb(51, 153, 102); ">Nos dimos casi pura ropa y para la estudiosa un librero</span></p>
<p><img alt="" src="https://s3-us-west-2.amazonaws.com/hectorykarla/2010/xmas13_sm_thumb.jpg" />&nbsp;&nbsp;<img alt="" src="https://s3-us-west-2.amazonaws.com/hectorykarla/2010/xmas14_sm_thumb.jpg" /></p>
<p>&nbsp;</p>
<p>See also [[[New Years Eve 2010]]] / &nbsp;Las fotos del a&ntilde;o nuevo [[[New Years Eve 2010]]]</p>','https://s3-us-west-2.amazonaws.com/hectorykarla/2010/xmas03_sm_thumb.jpg','2010-12-24',2010,'Christmas 2010','e4067030-5886-4adf-9559-63fa6a4b8095');
