INSERT INTO blogs VALUES(90,'2009-snow-day','Snow Day','2014-11-18 02:11:27.985957','2015-12-20 14:20:30.163469','<p>After an&nbsp;unseasonal warm second half of February we got several inches of snow on the 28th. I guess this will be the last snow of the year.</p>
<p><span style="color: rgb(51, 153, 102); ">A pesar de que las ultimas dos semanas de febrero tuvimos un clima bastante calido comparado con otros a&ntilde;os, justo el dia 28 nos toco una buena nevada y nos calleron varias pulgadas de nieve.</span></p>
<p>&nbsp;</p>
<p>This is just outside our house. / <span style="color: rgb(51, 153, 102); ">Justo afuera de la casa</span></p>
