<p><img alt="" border="1" src="https://s3-us-west-2.amazonaws.com/hectorykarla/2009/PC310068_thumb.JPG" />&nbsp;<img alt="" border="1" src="https://s3-us-west-2.amazonaws.com/hectorykarla/2009/PC310073_thumb.JPG" />&nbsp;</p>
<p><img alt="" border="1" src="https://s3-us-west-2.amazonaws.com/hectorykarla/2009/PC310074_thumb.JPG" />&nbsp;<img alt="" border="1" src="https://s3-us-west-2.amazonaws.com/hectorykarla/2009/PC310077_thumb.JPG" />&nbsp;</p>
<p><img alt="" border="1" src="https://s3-us-west-2.amazonaws.com/hectorykarla/2009/PC310079_thumb.JPG" />&nbsp;<img alt="" border="1" src="https://s3-us-west-2.amazonaws.com/hectorykarla/2009/PC310086_thumb.JPG" />&nbsp;</p>
<p><img alt="" border="1" src="https://s3-us-west-2.amazonaws.com/hectorykarla/2009/PC310090_thumb.JPG" />&nbsp;</p>
<p>&nbsp;</p>
<p>We did a lot of birdwatching. We saw mostly chickadees, junkos and blue jays coming to the bird feeder outside the cabin. There was a squirrel that claim ownership of that tree and fought with the blue jays. It was quite a show to see it leap after the birds!</p>
<p><img alt="" border="1" src="https://s3-us-west-2.amazonaws.com/hectorykarla/2009/P1010121_thumb.JPG" />&nbsp;<img alt="" border="1" src="https://s3-us-west-2.amazonaws.com/hectorykarla/2009/P1020175_thumb.JPG" />&nbsp;<img alt="" border="1" src="https://s3-us-west-2.amazonaws.com/hectorykarla/2009/P1020192_thumb.JPG" />&nbsp;</p>
<p><img alt="" border="1" src="https://s3-us-west-2.amazonaws.com/hectorykarla/2009/P1030241_thumb.JPG" />&nbsp;<img alt="" border="1" src="https://s3-us-west-2.amazonaws.com/hectorykarla/2009/P1030249_thumb.JPG" />&nbsp;</p>
<p>Hector went for&nbsp;walks and saw ice fishing and some deer.</p>
<p>&nbsp;<img alt="" border="1" src="https://s3-us-west-2.amazonaws.com/hectorykarla/2009/P1010123_thumb.JPG" />&nbsp;<img alt="" border="1" src="https://s3-us-west-2.amazonaws.com/hectorykarla/2009/P1010130_thumb.JPG" />&nbsp;</p>
