<p><img alt="" border="1" src="https://s3-us-west-2.amazonaws.com/hectorykarla/2009/NewYearA_174_thumb.JPG" />&nbsp;<img alt="" border="1" src="https://s3-us-west-2.amazonaws.com/hectorykarla/2009/NewYearA_175_thumb.JPG" />&nbsp;</p>
