INSERT INTO blogs VALUES(93,'2008-christmas','Christmas','2014-11-18 02:11:28.059323','2014-11-18 02:11:28.059323','<p>On Christmas Eve we got together with Eric and Geovanna for dinner. /&nbsp;<span style="color: rgb(51, 153, 102); ">El 24 la pasamos con Eric y Geovanna.</span><span style="color: rgb(0, 51, 0); ">&nbsp;</span></p>
<p><img border="1" width="260" height="195" alt="" src="https://s3-us-west-2.amazonaws.com/hectorykarla/2008/xmaspb200011_thumb.jpg" />&nbsp;<img border="1" width="260" height="173" alt="" src="https://s3-us-west-2.amazonaws.com/hectorykarla/2008/xmaseve_thumb.jpg" /></p>
<p>Eric and Geovanna finishing up the ham / <span style="color: rgb(51, 153, 102); ">Eric y Geovana dandole los ultimos toques al jamon.</span></p>
<p><img border="1" alt="" src="https://s3-us-west-2.amazonaws.com/hectorykarla/2008/xmaspb200008_thumb.jpg" />&nbsp;<img border="1" alt="" src="https://s3-us-west-2.amazonaws.com/hectorykarla/2008/xmaspb200003_thumb.jpg" /></p>
<p>Karla did the Turkey and Chocolate Mouse / <span style="color: rgb(51, 153, 102); ">Karla cocino un rico pavito y un mousse de chocolate de postre.</span></p>
<p><img border="1" alt="" src="https://s3-us-west-2.amazonaws.com/hectorykarla/2008/xmaspb200001_thumb.jpg" />&nbsp;<img border="1" alt="" src="https://s3-us-west-2.amazonaws.com/hectorykarla/2008/xmaspb200014_thumb.jpg" />&nbsp;&nbsp;</p>
<p><img border="1" alt="" src="https://s3-us-west-2.amazonaws.com/hectorykarla/2008/xmaspb200007_thumb.jpg" />&nbsp;<img border="1" alt="" src="https://s3-us-west-2.amazonaws.com/hectorykarla/2008/xmaspb200002_thumb.jpg" />&nbsp;</p>
<p><img border="1" alt="" src="https://s3-us-west-2.amazonaws.com/hectorykarla/2008/xmaspb200010_thumb.jpg" />&nbsp;&nbsp;</p>
<p>After dinner we played dominos with and exchanged presents. We had a great time. <span style="color: rgb(51, 153, 102); ">/ Despues de la cena jugamos domino e intercambiamos regalos, nos la pasamos a todo dar.</span></p>
<h3>...back at home / de regreso a casa</h3>
<p>Later that night we came back home, called our parents and opened the presents that Santa had left under our Christmas tree. We realized we hadn''t taken any pictures of our tree this year so we made up for it by taking tons of pictures in one night. Trying to take pictures with two dogs in the house is far more challenging that it looks but also a lot of fun. / <span style="color: rgb(51, 153, 102); ">Despues de la cena con Eric y Geovana regresamos a la casa, llamamos a nuestros papas y esperamos a que dieran las 12 para abrir los regalitos que Santa dejo en nuestro arbolito. Como no habiamos tomado fotos de nuestro arbolito este a&ntilde;o hicimos una sesion fotografica con todo y perros.</span></p>
