INSERT INTO blogs VALUES(96,'2008-paris-2008-day-12','Paris 2008 Day 12','2014-11-18 02:11:28.149215','2014-11-18 02:11:28.149215','<p>Wednesday August 13/ <span style="color: #339966">Miercoles 13 de&nbsp;agosto</span></p>
<p>We&nbsp;went to the d''Orsay Museum, especialized in Impressionists, and spent the day there. After that we went to see the exterior of the Opera Garnier (it was close to closing time for inside tours). This is where the Phantom of the Opera did his haunting. Then, we had&nbsp;a drink at Cafe de la Paix,&nbsp;designed also&nbsp;by Garnier. In the evening we went back to Jardin&nbsp;des Plantes and had dinner at the same place. It was again a decadent experience.</p>
<p><span style="color: #339966">Fuimos al museo d''Orsay, especializado en arte Impresionista, y pasamos el dia ahi. De ahi nos fuimos a ver la fachada de la Opera Garnier, de donde es el Fantasma de la Opera. Era casi hora de cerrar para visitas al interior, asi que nos fuimos enfrente, al Cafe de la Paz, disenado por el mismo Garnier, a tomar una copa. En la noche regresamos al barrio de Jardin des Plantes a cenar en el mismo restaurante, y fue de nuevo una experiencia maravillosa.</span></p>
<p>&nbsp;<a href="javascript:viewpicture(''Paris+2008'',''pictures/2008/p8131070.jpg'')"><img alt="" border="1" src="https://s3-us-west-2.amazonaws.com/hectorykarla/2008/p8131070_thumb.jpg" /></a>&nbsp; <a href="javascript:viewpicture(''Paris+2008'',''pictures/2008/p8131074.jpg'')"><img alt="" border="1" src="https://s3-us-west-2.amazonaws.com/hectorykarla/2008/p8131074_thumb.jpg" /></a>&nbsp; <a href="javascript:viewpicture(''Paris+2008'',''pictures/2008/p8131090.jpg'')"><img alt="" border="1" src="https://s3-us-west-2.amazonaws.com/hectorykarla/2008/p8131090_thumb.jpg" /></a>&nbsp; <a href="javascript:viewpicture(''Paris+2008'',''pictures/2008/p8131131.jpg'')"><img alt="" border="1" src="https://s3-us-west-2.amazonaws.com/hectorykarla/2008/p8131131_thumb.jpg" /></a>&nbsp; <a href="javascript:viewpicture(''Paris+2008'',''pictures/2008/p8131139.jpg'')"><img alt="" border="1" src="https://s3-us-west-2.amazonaws.com/hectorykarla/2008/p8131139_thumb.jpg" /></a>&nbsp; <a href="javascript:viewpicture(''Paris+2008'',''pictures/2008/p8131151.jpg'')"><img alt="" border="1" src="https://s3-us-west-2.amazonaws.com/hectorykarla/2008/p8131151_thumb.jpg" /></a>&nbsp; <a href="javascript:viewpicture(''Paris+2008'',''pictures/2008/img_4903.jpg'')"><img alt="" border="1" src="https://s3-us-west-2.amazonaws.com/hectorykarla/2008/img_4903_thumb.jpg" /></a>&nbsp; <a href="javascript:viewpicture(''Paris+2008'',''pictures/2008/p8131200.jpg'')"><img alt="" border="1" src="https://s3-us-west-2.amazonaws.com/hectorykarla/2008/p8131200_thumb.jpg" /></a>&nbsp; <a href="javascript:viewpicture(''Paris+2008'',''pictures/2008/p8131209.jpg'')"><img alt="" border="1" src="https://s3-us-west-2.amazonaws.com/hectorykarla/2008/p8131209_thumb.jpg" /></a>&nbsp; <a href="javascript:viewpicture(''Paris+2008'',''pictures/2008/p8131210.jpg'')"><img alt="" border="1" src="https://s3-us-west-2.amazonaws.com/hectorykarla/2008/p8131210_thumb.jpg" /></a>&nbsp; <a href="javascript:viewpicture(''Paris+2008'',''pi