INSERT INTO blogs VALUES(101,'2008-paris-2008-day-13','Paris 2008 Day 13','2014-11-18 02:11:28.244650','2014-11-18 02:11:28.244650','<p>Thursday, August 14/<span style="color: #339966">Jueves 14 de agosto</span></p>
<p>It was cold in the morning as we went to the park behind Notre Dame, so&nbsp;Karla had to go and buy a sweater. We walked around the Chatelet and west Marais area, saw the Pompideu Center and stopped in a cafe for a cosmo and a coffee.&nbsp; In the afternoon we went to the Latin Quarter for dinner, and on our way there we saw a procession coming out of Notre Dame due to the Asuncion''s Day.&nbsp; After dinner we went into a Piano bar and had a wonderful time.</p>
<p><span style="color: #339966">Hizo frio en la manana cuando fuimos al parque detras de Notre Dame, asi que Karla tuvo que comprarse un sweater. Caminamos por el barrio de Chatelet y la parte oeste del Marais, y vimos el Centro Pompideu, y paramos a tomar un cafe y un cosmo. En la tarde fuimos al barrio latino a cenar, y de ida vimos una peregrinacion a la virgen de la Asuncion. Despues de la cena llegamos a un piano bar donde nos divertimos de lo lindo.</span></p>
<p><a href="javascript:viewpicture(''Paris+2008'',''pictures/2008/p8141233.jpg'')"><img alt="" border="1" src="https://s3-us-west-2.amazonaws.com/hectorykarla/2008/p8141233_thumb.jpg" /></a>&nbsp;<a href="javascript:viewpicture(''Paris+2008'',''pictures/2008/p8141234.jpg'')"><img alt="" border="1" src="https://s3-us-west-2.amazonaws.com/hectorykarla/2008/p8141234_thumb.jpg" /></a></p>
