INSERT INTO blogs VALUES(107,'2008-paris-2008-day-6','Paris 2008 Day 6','2014-11-18 02:11:28.361757','2014-11-18 02:11:28.361757','<p><span>Thursday, August 7/</span><span style="color: #339966"><span>Jueves 7 de agosto</span></span></p>
<p><span>After lunch (sandwiches) by the river,&nbsp;we went to see St Severin''s church. As most churches in Paris, this one also has the stained glass windows, nice columns,&nbsp;vaulted ceilings, overall gothic style and gargoyles outside. Saint Severin also has a unique twisted column behind the altar. We decided to take a break back at the hotel and as soon as we arrived, we received a nice surprise from some friends from Kansas City: a bottle of champagne.&nbsp;We brought out the grapes and cheese from&nbsp;our mini-refrigerator and enjoyed it in our balcony, seeing the sunset and rainbow after the rain. La vie en rose! </span></p>
<p><span>That evening we walked back to the Marais to a Middle Eastern restaurant. We didn''t understand a word, so we went into the kitchen to point to the items we wanted in our sampler plate: feta cheese, chicken livers, tapenade, tuna, artichokes, meatballs, tomato and celery salad, with black bread and red wine. It rained as we ate under the awning.</span></p>
<p><span style="color: #339966">Lonchamos unos sandwiches en el rio y nos fuimos a la iglesia de San Severin. La mayoria de las iglesias de Paris tienen vitrales, columnas y techos abovedados, estilo gotico con gargolas afuera. San Severin, ademas de eso, tiene una rara columna torcida detras del altar.&nbsp; Como estabamos cansados, decidimos regresar al hotel, donde recibimos una grata sorpresa: una botella de champana que unos amigos de Kansas City nos mandaron. Sacamos lo que nos quedaba de uvas y quedo del frigobar y nos tomamos la champana en el balcon, viendo el atardecer y arcoiris que salio al terminar la lluvia. La vida en rosa!!!</span></p>
<p><span style="color: #339966">Esa noche caminamos de regreso a Marais a un restaurante del medio oriente, a cenar. Como no entendiamos nada de la carta, nos metimos a la cocina a apuntar que queriamos&nbsp;en&nbsp;nuestro plato de bocadillos:&nbsp;queso feta, higaditos de pollo,&nbsp;pure de aceitunas, atun, alcachofas, albondigas, ensalada de&nbsp;jitomate&nbsp;con apio, y pan negro&nbsp;con vino tinto. Llovio mientras comiamos&nbsp;bajo el caidizo&nbsp;del restaurante.&nbsp;</span></p>
<p><span style="color: #339966"><font color="#000000">&nbsp; </font><a href="javascript:viewpicture(''Paris+2008'',''pictures/2008/p8070438.jpg'')"><font color="#000000"><img alt="" border="1" src="https://s3-us-west-2.amazonaws.com/hectorykarla/2008/p8070438_thumb.jpg" /></font></a><font color="#000000">&nbsp; </font><a href="javascript:viewpicture(''Paris+2008'',''pictures/2008/p8070444.jpg'')"><font color="#000000"><img alt="" border="1" src="https://s3-us-west-2.amazonaws.com/hectorykarla/2008/p8070444_thumb.jpg" /></font></a><font color="#000000">&nbsp; </font><a href="javascript:viewpicture(''Paris+2008'',''pictures/2008/p8070447.jpg'')"><font color="#000000"><img alt="" border="1" src="https://s3-us-west-2.amazonaws.com/hectorykarla/2008/p8070447_thumb.jpg" /></font></a><font color="#000000">&nbsp; </font><a href="javascript:viewpicture(''Paris+2008'',''pictures/2008/p8070453.jpg'')"><font color="#000000"><img alt="" border="1" src="https://s3-us-west-2.amazonaws.com/hectorykarla/2008/p8070453_thumb.jpg" /></font></a><font color="#000000">&nbsp; </font><a href="javascript:viewpicture(''Paris+2008'',''pictures/2008/p8070464.jpg'')"><font color="#000000"><img alt="" border="1" src="https://s3-us-west-2.amazonaws.com/hectorykarla/2008/p8070464_thumb.jpg" /></font></a><font color="#000000">&nbsp; </font><a href="javascript:viewpicture(''Paris+2008'',''pictures/2008/p8070471.jpg'')"><font color="#000000"><img alt="" border="1" src="https://s3-us-west-2.amazonaws.com/hectorykarla/2008/p8070471_thumb.jpg" /></font></a><font color="#000000">&nbsp; </font><a href="javascript:viewpicture(''Paris+2008'',''pictures/2008/img_4701.jpg'')"><font color="#000000"><img alt="" border="1" src="https://s3-us-west-2.amazonaws.com/hectorykarla/2008/img_4701_thumb.jpg" /></font></a><font color="#000000">&nbsp; </font><a href="javascript:viewpicture(''Paris+2008'',''pictures/2008/img_4707.jpg'')"><font color="#000000"><img alt="" border="1" src="https://s3-us-west-2.amazonaws.com/hectorykarla/2008/img_4707_thumb.jpg" /></font></a><font color="#000000">&nbsp; </font><a href="javascript:viewpicture(''Paris+2008'',''pictures/2008/p8070486.jpg'')"><font color="#000000"><img alt="" border="1" src="https://s3-us-west-2.amazonaws.com/hectorykarla/2008/p8070486_thumb.jpg" /></font></a><font color="#000000">&nbsp; </font><a href="javascript:viewpicture(''Paris+2008'',''pictures/2008/p8070489.jpg'')"><font color="#000000"><img alt="" border="1" src="https://s3-us-west-2.amazonaws.com/hectorykarla/2008/p8070489_thumb.jpg" /></font></a><font color="#000000">&nbsp; </font><a href="javascript:viewpicture(''Paris+2008'',''pictures/2008/p8070490.jpg'')"><img alt="" border="1" src="https://s3-us-west-2.amazonaws.com/hectorykarla/2008/p8070490_thumb.jpg" /></a></span></p>
