INSERT INTO blogs VALUES(108,'2008-paris-2008-day-5','Paris 2008 Day 5','2014-11-18 02:11:28.380125','2014-11-18 02:11:28.380125','<p>Wednesday, August 6/<span style="color: #339966">Miercoles 6 de agosto</span></p>
<p><span>We did some shopping (mostly window shopping) around the hotel and across the Louvre. After that, we lounged, read and napped at the Tuleries gardens. It was a hot day and we just rested for hours, until we were ready for a mango ice cream. In the late afernoon we walked along the Seine,&nbsp;to the Latin Quarter where we had dinner. At 9:00 p.m. we went to a concert at St-Julien-le-Pauvre''s church: music of Django Reinheardt by Frederic Belinsky.</span></p>
<p><span style="color: #339966">En la manana fuimos de compras (y a bobear) a tiendas cerca del hotel y del museo del Louvre. De ahi nos fuimos a los jardines de las Tullerias (afuera del museo) donde pasamos horas leyendo, descansando y hasta dormitando. Hizo calor, asi que compramos nieve de mango de nuevo. En la trade regresamos caminando a lo largo del rio Sena hacia el barrio latino, donde cenamos. A las 9:00 fuimos a un concierto en la iglesia de San Julien-le-Pauvre, con Federico Belinsky tocando musica de Django Reinhardt.</span></p>
<p><span style="color: #339966"><a href="javascript:viewpicture(''Paris+2008'',''pictures/2008/p8060378.jpg'')"><font color="#000000"><img alt="" border="1" src="https://s3-us-west-2.amazonaws.com/hectorykarla/2008/p8060378_thumb.jpg" /></font></a><font color="#000000">&nbsp; </font><a href="javascript:viewpicture(''Paris+2008'',''pictures/2008/p8060386.jpg'')"><font color="#000000"><img alt="" border="1" src="https://s3-us-west-2.amazonaws.com/hectorykarla/2008/p8060386_thumb.jpg" /></font></a><font color="#000000">&nbsp; </font><a href="javascript:viewpicture(''Paris+2008'',''pictures/2008/p8060391.jpg'')"><font color="#000000"><img alt="" border="1" src="https://s3-us-west-2.amazonaws.com/hectorykarla/2008/p8060391_thumb.jpg" /></font></a><font color="#000000">&nbsp; </font><a href="javascript:viewpicture(''Paris+2008'',''pictures/2008/p8060394.jpg'')"><font color="#000000"><img alt="" border="1" src="https://s3-us-west-2.amazonaws.com/hectorykarla/2008/p8060394_thumb.jpg" /></font></a><font color="#000000">&nbsp; </font><a href="javascript:viewpicture(''Paris+2008'',''pictures/2008/img_4693.jpg'')"><font color="#000000"><img alt="" border="1" src="https://s3-us-west-2.amazonaws.com/hectorykarla/2008/img_4693_thumb.jpg" /></font></a><font color="#000000">&nbsp; </font><a href="javascript:viewpicture(''Paris+2008'',''pictures/2008/p8060403.jpg'')"><font color="#000000"><img alt="" border="1" src="https://s3-us-west-2.amazonaws.com/hectorykarla/2008/p8060403_thumb.jpg" /></font></a><font color="#000000">&nbsp; </font><a href="javascript:viewpicture(''Paris+2008'',''pictures/2008/img_4700.jpg'')"><font color="#000000"><img alt="" border="1" src="https://s3-us-west-2.amazonaws.com/hectorykarla/2008/img_4700_thumb.jpg" /></font></a><font color="#000000">&nbsp;</font></span></p>
