INSERT INTO blogs VALUES(110,'2008-paris-2008-day-3','Paris 2008 Day 3','2014-11-18 02:11:28.417528','2014-11-18 02:11:28.417528','<p>Monday August 4/<span style="color: #339966">Lunes 4 de agosto</span></p>
<p>After another 12 hours of sleep we got ready and took the bus to Champ de Mars, where the Eiffel Tower is, and Trocadero. We stayed there most of the day, reading, relaxing walking, people-watching, and taking tons of pictures of every single part of the tower. We walked around the neighborhood, on Rue Cler, and then took the Metro to the Latin Quarter and had dinner there (escargot, Confit de Canard, Lamb chops, chocolate mousse and ice cream).</p>
<p><span style="color: #339966">Despues de dormir 12 horas de nuevo nos levantamos y tomamos el camion a los campos de Marte, donde esta la torre Eiffel, y a Trocadero. Ahi pasamos el dia, leyendo, acostados en el pasto, caminando, bobeando y tomando miles de fotos de la torre. Luego caminamos por el barrio y tomamos el metro al barrio latino, donde cenamos (caracoles al ajo, pato, borrego, mousse de chocolate y nieve).</span></p>
