INSERT INTO blogs VALUES(113,'2008-knob-noster','Knob Noster','2014-11-18 02:11:28.483512','2014-11-18 02:11:28.483512','<p>This 4th of July weekend we went camping to Knob Noster State Park. We had a great time.</p>
<p>
  <img alt="" src="https://s3-us-west-2.amazonaws.com/hectorykarla/2008/knobnoster26_thumb.JPG" />
</p>
<p><strong>On the Discovery Trail</strong>.&nbsp;Hiking with&nbsp;the doggies. &nbsp;</p>
<p>
  <img alt="" src="https://s3-us-west-2.amazonaws.com/hectorykarla/2008/knobnoster01_thumb.JPG" />
  <img alt="" src="https://s3-us-west-2.amazonaws.com/hectorykarla/2008/knobnoster02_thumb.JPG" />
</p>
<p>Look at the size of those musrooms</p>
<p>
  <img alt="" src="https://s3-us-west-2.amazonaws.com/hectorykarla/2008/knobnoster03_thumb.JPG" />
  <img alt="" src="https://s3-us-west-2.amazonaws.com/hectorykarla/2008/knobnoster04_thumb.JPG" />
</p>
<p><strong>Back in the&nbsp;Campground</strong></p>
<p>
  <img alt="" src="https://s3-us-west-2.amazonaws.com/hectorykarla/2008/knobnoster05_thumb.JPG" />
  <img alt="" src="https://s3-us-west-2.amazonaws.com/hectorykarla/2008/knobnoster06_thumb.JPG" />
</p>
<p>Karla snatched this picture right from our campsite.</p>
<p>
  <img alt="" src="https://s3-us-west-2.amazonaws.com/hectorykarla/2008/knobnoster07_thumb.JPG" />
</p>
<p><strong>On the North Loop Trail</strong>. This is a two mile trail that was really neat,&nbsp;I am sure weather in the lower 80s with low humidity had something to do with it!,&nbsp;but check out the pictures so you know what I mean.</p>
<p>
  <img alt="" src="https://s3-us-west-2.amazonaws.com/hectorykarla/2008/knobnoster08_thumb.JPG" />
  <img alt="" src="https://s3-us-west-2.amazonaws.com/hectorykarla/2008/knobnoster09_thumb.JPG" />
  <img alt="" src="https://s3-us-west-2.amazonaws.com/hectorykarla/2008/knobnoster10_thumb.JPG" />
  <img alt="" border="1" src="https://s3-us-west-2.amazonaws.com/hectorykarla/2008/knobnoster11_thumb.JPG" />
  <img alt="" src="https://s3-us-west-2.amazonaws.com/hectorykarla/2008/knobnoster12_thumb.JPG" />
  <img alt="" src="https://s3-us-west-2.amazonaws.com/hectorykarla/2008/knobnoster14_thumb.JPG" />
  <img alt="" src="https://s3-us-west-2.amazonaws.com/hectorykarla/2008/knobnoster16_thumb.JPG" />
  </p>
<p>Can you spot the bird?&nbsp;</p>
<p>
  <img alt="" src="https://s3-us-west-2.amazonaws.com/hectorykarla/2008/knobnoster17_thumb.JPG" />
</p>
<p>
  <img alt="" src="https://s3-us-west-2.amazonaws.com/hectorykarla/2008/knobnoster18_thumb.JPG" />
  <img alt="" src="https://s3-us-west-2.amazonaws.com/hectorykarla/2008/knobnoster20_thumb.JPG" />
  </p>
<p>Another mushroom (this one a tiny one) -- I didn''t bite it, it was like that when I got there.</p>
<p>
  <img alt="" src="https://s3-us-west-2.amazonaws.com/hectorykarla/2008/knobnoster21_thumb.JPG" />
</p>
<p>Another birdie right on our campsite&nbsp;</p>
<p style="text-align: center">
  <img alt="" src="https://s3-us-west-2.amazonaws.com/hectorykarla/2008/knobnoster22_thumb.JPG" />
</p>
<p>Finally, dogs tired!</p>
<p style="text-align: center">
  <img alt="" src="https://s3-us-west-2.amazonaws.com/hectorykarla/2008/knobnoster23_thumb.JPG" />
</p>
<p>Our camping stove broke on Saturday morning so we spent all Saturday and early
Sunday cooking on the fire. They sold firewood in the campground but with all the
rain that we''ve been getting this year&nbsp;the wood&nbsp;was somewhat wet and it
really forced us to work hard to start our fires. Talk about a real camping experience!
Here we are keeping the coffee warm.</p>
<p>
  <img alt="" src="https://s3-us-west-2.amazonaws.com/hectorykarla/2008/knobnoster24_thumb.JPG" />
  <img alt="" src="https://s3-us-west-2.amazonaws.com/hectorykarla/2008/knobnoster25_thumb.JPG" />
</p>




',NULL,'2008-07-08',2008,'Knob Noster 2008','b07ec46e-338e-4440-8ade-65e40865fd6f');
