INSERT INTO blogs VALUES(128,'2007-ku-graduation','KU Graduation','2014-11-18 02:11:28.872565','2015-12-20 15:20:09.519167','<p>Here are the pictures from Karla''s graduation at KU. She participated in two events, one on Saturday, with a formal ceremony by the School of Education, and one on Sunday, an informal walk into the stadium with all 6,000 KU graduating students. She received her Master of Science in Higher Educacion. Well, almost. She still has two&nbsp;elective classes to take and will receive her diploma in December.&nbsp;Click on each picture to enlarge.</p>
<p><font color="#339966">Estas son las fotos de la graduacion de Karla. Ella participo en dos eventos. Uno fue la ceremonia formal de la escuela de educacion el sabado, y el otro fue la caminada al estadio del domingo, con otros 6,000 estudiantes de la universidad de Kansas. Karla recibio su Maestria en Educacion Superior. Bueno, casi. Todavia le quedan dos clases electivas por completar; le dan su diploma en diciembre. Ha</font><font color="#339966">z click en las fotos para agrandarlas. </font></p>
<p>&nbsp;</p>
<p><font size="4">Saturday, May 19th, 2007/<font color="#339966">Sabado 19 de mayo del 2007</font></font></p>
<p>At home, getting ready. <font color="#339966">En la casa, alistandome.</font></p>
<p><a href="javascript:viewpicture(''KU Graduation 2007'',''pictures/2007/graduation003.jpg'')"><img alt="" border="1" src="https://s3-us-west-2.amazonaws.com/hectorykarla/2007/graduation003_thumb.jpg" /></a>&nbsp;</p>
<p>Arriving to the Lied Center, where the ceremony for the school of Education took place. With Anita, Nancy, David, and Hector.</p>
<p><font color="#339966">Llegando al auditorio donde fue la ceremonia de graduacion de la escuela de educacion. Con Anita, Nancy, David, y Hector.</font></p>
<p><a href="javascript:viewpicture(''KU Graduation 2007'',''pictures/2007/graduation005.jpg'')"><img alt="" border="1" src="https://s3-us-west-2.amazonaws.com/hectorykarla/2007/graduation005_thumb.jpg" /></a> <a href="javascript:viewpicture(''KU Graduation 2007'',''pictures/2007/graduation006.jpg'')"><img alt="" border="1" src="https://s3-us-west-2.amazonaws.com/hectorykarla/2007/graduation006_thumb.jpg" /></a>&nbsp;</p>
<p><a href="javascript:viewpicture(''KU Graduation 2007'',''pictures/2007/graduation008.jpg'')"><img alt="" border="1" src="https://s3-us-west-2.amazonaws.com/hectorykarla/2007/graduation008_thumb.jpg" /></a>&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="javascript:viewpicture(''KU Graduation 2007'',''pictures/2007/graduation009.jpg'')"><img alt="" border="1" src="https://s3-us-west-2.amazonaws.com/hectorykarla/2007/graduation009_thumb.jpg" /></a> <a href="javascript:viewpicture(''KU Graduation 2007'',''pictures/2007/graduation010.jpg'')"><img alt="" border="1" src="https://s3-us-west-2.amazonaws.com/hectorykarla/2007/graduation010_thumb.jpg" /></a> <a href="javascript:viewpicture(''KU Graduation 2007'',''pictures/2007/graduation011.jpg'')"><img alt="" border="1" src="https://s3-us-west-2.amazonaws.com/hectorykarla/2007/graduation011_thumb.jpg" /></a> <a href="javascript:viewpicture(''KU Graduation 2007'',''pictures/2007/graduation105.jpg'')"><img alt="" border="1" src="https://s3-us-west-2.amazonaws.com/hectorykarla/2007/graduation105_thumb.jpg" /></a> <a href="javascript:viewpicture(''KU Graduation 2007'',''pictures/2007/graduation106.jpg'')"><img alt="" border="1" src="https://s3-us-west-2.amazonaws.com/hectorykarla/2007/graduation106_thumb.jpg" /></a> <a href="javascript:viewpicture(''KU Graduation 2007'',''pictures/2007/graduation107.jpg'')"><img alt="" border="1" src="https://s3-us-west-2.amazonaws.com/hectorykarla/2007/graduation107_thumb.jpg" /></a> <a href="javascript:viewpicture(''KU Graduation 2007'',''pictures/2007/graduation108.jpg'')"><img alt="" border="1" src="https://s3-us-west-2.amazonaws.com/hectorykarla/2007/graduation108_thumb.jpg" /></a></p>
<p>Inside the Lied Center. There were bachelors, masters, EdD and PhD graduating students, all from the School of Education.</p>
<p><font color="#339966">Adentro del auditorio. Habia graduados de licenciatura, maestria, y doctorado, todos de la escuela de educacion.</font></p>
