INSERT INTO blogs VALUES(130,'2007-loose-park','Loose Park','2014-11-18 02:11:28.910499','2015-12-20 15:23:10.174009','<p><br />
<br />
This Winter has been really cold here in Kansas City. The temperature has stayed on the 20s for 3 or 4 weeks! The nice thing about it is that there is a great scenary around the city with a combination of ice and snow.<br />
<br />
I took these pictures at <a target="_blank" href="http://www.kcmo.org/parks.nsf/web/loose?opendocument">Loose Park</a> on February 3rd. The snow that you see in these pictures has been here since we took the [[[Snow Day 2007]]] pictures.</p>
<p><font color="#339966">Este invierno si que ha estado frio aqui en Kansas City, ya tenemos varias semanas en que la temperatura esta alrededor de 12 grados Centigrados bajo cero &iexcl;todo el dia! Lo bueno de todo esto es que la nieve que nos ha caido se ha quedado con nostros y la ciudad se ve hermosa. Las fotos de esta pagina las tome en Loose Park el 3 de febrero y es la misma nieve que aparece en la pagina [[[Snow Day 2007]]]</font></p>
<p><br />
