INSERT INTO blogs VALUES(181,'2003-mac-pictures','Mac Pictures','2014-11-18 02:11:29.951686','2015-05-25 20:05:17.561442','<h4>Introducing Mac/Con ustedes Mac</h4>
On Monday, May 26th we got a new dog. His name is Mac. He is a yellow Lab like Summer. He was born on March 6 and weights 24 lbs.

Since the moment he met Summer he was ready to play with her. Summer usually scares and tires other dogs because she is very hyper and playful. Mac doesn''t get impressed by her height and tries really hard to teach her a lesson. Summer has been very gentle and patient.

Mac and Summer have the same color, even in the stripes. But his nose is brown and his eyes are greenish brown. As expected, during the night we needed to wake up a couple of times to take Mac out for potty. Going back to sleep was an adventure of its own. During the day, Summer barely lets him sleep with all the playing and running, but he seems happy to be here with us. We hope Summer calms down a bit now that she has a partner to play with.

Here are a few pictures of the new baby in the family: Mac Loya.
<hr>
<div class=spanish>El lunes 26 de mayo compramos otro perro, se llama Mac y es, al igual que Summer, un Labrador amarillo. Nació el 6 de marzo y pesa 10 kilos.

Por lo general Summer asusta o cansa a otros perros fácilmente porque es super juguetona. Mac no se asusta y no se le deja, pero se cansa rápido. Es divertido verlo tratar de arrebatarle un hueso a Summer. Summer es cuidadosa y cariñosa con él.

Ambos perros tienen el mismo color de pelo pero la nariz de él es café y sus ojos son claros. Durante su primera noche con nosotros, nos tuvimos que levantar varias veces para sacarlo a hacer pipi, convencerlo de que siga dormido despues de eso fue toda una aventura. Durante el día Summer casi no lo deja dormir con todo el juegueteo y carreras que pegan, pero se le ve feliz. Esperamos que Summer se tranquilice ahora que tiene con quien jugar.

Aquí están unas fotos del nuevo bebé de la familia: Mac Loya.</div>
