INSERT INTO blogs VALUES(191,'2002-new-house-moving-day','New House Moving Day','2014-11-18 02:11:30.180477','2015-05-25 20:41:47.434421','<h3>Moving Day/La Mudanza...</h3>
<table>
    <tbody>
        <tr>
            <td>Hector with a big smile after driving the truck from Mastin to Rockhill. The smile faded away after they told me that I should have parked in our neighbor&rsquo;s driveway and in reverse! Oh well...  Hector feliz y contento despues de haber manejado el camion del departamento a la casa. Lo feliz se me quito cuando me dijeron que mejor me estacionara en la cochera del vecino y &iexcl;en reversa! En fin...</td>
            <td><img alt="" src="https://s3-us-west-2.amazonaws.com/hectorykarla/2002/movingday/truck1.jpg" /></td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
            <td>After several failed attempts, I finally parked that big (it felt gigantic) truck in reverse to make the unloading easy for our crew &ndash; picky, just picky people :)  Ahora si, despues de varios intentos fallidos, aqui esta el camioncito estacionado en reversa para facilitarles la descarga a nuestro equipo &ndash; bola de delicados :)</td>
