INSERT INTO blogs VALUES(195,'2002-halloween-party','Halloween Party','2014-11-18 02:11:30.252776','2015-05-25 20:48:31.362865','<h3>Halloween Party Nov. 1, 2002 Fiesta de Dia de Brujas. 1 de noviembre del 2002</h3>
<p>Welcome to our Halloween Party. Sincerely, your hosts, The Jester and the Lady from the Last Century. Bienvenidos a nuestra fiesta del D&iacute;a de Brujas. Atentamente, El Buf&oacute;n y la Se&ntilde;ora del siglo pasado. <img border="1" alt="" src="https://s3-us-west-2.amazonaws.com/hectorykarla/2002/halloween/hector_karla.jpg" /></p>
<hr />
<p>Martha Stewart, who won the Best Costume prize and a wounded guy (who didn&rsquo;t feel too bad to stop drinking) and his wife. (they are our neighbors.) Martha Stewart, una persona famosa en TV, y un chavo todo herido J que no se sent&iacute;a tan mal porque estaba tomando vino, con su esposa. Ellos son nuestros vecinos. <img height="277" width="507" border="1" alt="" src="https://s3-us-west-2.amazonaws.com/hectorykarla/2002/halloween/nicole2.jpg" /></p>
<hr />
<p>An odd couple: a cheetah and a little wabbit... Extra&ntilde;a pareja: un leopardo y un conejo... <img border="1" alt="" src="https://s3-us-west-2.amazonaws.com/hectorykarla/2002/halloween/chris_claire.jpg" /></p>
<hr />
<p>A worker with two monkeys. Una trabajadora con dos changos. <img border="1" alt="" src="https://s3-us-west-2.amazonaws.com/hectorykarla/2002/halloween/hector_kathy.jpg" /></p>
<hr />
<p>In the middle you can see a Hobbit, I think it was Master Samwise, from Lord of the Rings. En medio esta un Hobbit, creo que Sam, del Se&ntilde;or de los Anillos. <img border="1" alt="" src="https://s3-us-west-2.amazonaws.com/hectorykarla/2002/halloween/scott_anita_heather.jpg" /></p>
<hr />
<p>Karla next to an FBI agent, who was drinking grape juice. Karla junto una agente del FBI, que estaba tomando jugo de uva, no sean mal pensados. <img border="1" alt="" src="https://s3-us-west-2.amazonaws.com/hectorykarla/2002/halloween/karina_karla.jpg" /></p>
<hr />
<p>Our handy dandy tool guy, ready to fix anything in the house. Nuestro maistro chido con las herramientas, por si algo se descompone. <img border="1" alt="" src="https://s3-us-west-2.amazonaws.com/hectorykarla/2002/halloween/sharla.jpg" /></p>
<hr />
<p>Agents Mulder and Scully, and the FBI girl were keeping a close watch on all of us. Los agentes Mulder y Scully y la chava del FBI nos ten&iacute;an checaditos. <img border="1" alt="" src="https://s3-us-west-2.amazonaws.com/hectorykarla/2002/halloween/hector_david_nancy.jpg" /></p>
<hr />
<p>The Hobbit won a cool fish for Most Creative Costume. La Hobbit se saco un pez de premio por el disfraz m&aacute;s creativo. <img border="1" alt="" src="https://s3-us-west-2.amazonaws.com/hectorykarla/2002/halloween/anita.jpg" /></p>
<hr />
<p>Princess Leah got confused after a few drinks and thought she was the Statue of the Liberty J La Princesa Leah despu&eacute;s de unas copitas se cre&iacute;a la Estatua de la Libertad J <img border="1" alt="" src="https://s3-us-west-2.amazonaws.com/hectorykarla/2002/halloween/heather.jpg" /></p>
<hr />
<p>Check the ribbons on the chain... Martha was giving us advice about the Stock Market. Hasta listones se puso Martha en las cadenas, para verse bien en la c&aacute;rcel. <img border="1" alt="" src="https://s3-us-west-2.amazonaws.com/hectorykarla/2002/halloween/nicole.jpg" /></p>
<hr />
<p>Kathy won the Scariest Costume. You cannot see it, but she had a few critters hanging from her back, a rat in the front and a spider in her ear. Kathy se saco el premio por el disfraz mas aterrador. No se ve, pero tenia unos bichos colgando de atr&aacute;s, una rata al frente y una ara&ntilde;a en la oreja. <img border="1" alt="" src="https://s3-us-west-2.amazonaws.com/hectorykarla/2002/halloween/kathy.jpg" /></p>
<hr />
<p>My Jester got the Funniest prize. Mi buf&oacute;n se saco el premio al disfraz m&aacute;s chistoso. <img border="1" alt="" src="https://s3-us-west-2.amazonaws.com/hectorykarla/2002/halloween/hector.jpg" /></p>
<hr />
<p>The Jester with the Scary Lady in PJ&rsquo;s. El buf&oacute;n con la se&ntilde;ora en pijamas que asusta. <img border="1" alt="" src="https://s3-us-west-2.amazonaws.com/hectorykarla/2002/halloween/hector_lena.jpg" /></p>
<hr />
<p>After the party, Summer was allowed back in the house and she even got to clean the leftovers J Despues de la fiesta, trajimos de regreso a Summer a que limpiara las sobras J <img border="1" alt="" src="https://s3-us-west-2.amazonaws.com/hectorykarla/2002/halloween/summer_karina.jpg" /></p>
<hr />
<p>One last shot with most of the creatures and celebrities that attended our party. Una ultima foto con la mayoria de las criaturas y famosos que vinieron a la fiesta. <img width="85%" border="1" alt="" src="https://s3-us-west-2.amazonaws.com/hectorykarla/2002/halloween/house123.jpg" /></p>','','2002-11-01',2002,'Halloween Party 2002','4bcdc21d-658a-400a-9e11-80e3dbfa3a90');
