INSERT INTO blogs VALUES(218,'2014-thanksgiving','Thanksgiving','2014-11-18 13:32:12.402904','2015-01-02 18:41:36.751217','<h2>Wednesday, November 26th.</h2>

<p>On Wednesday we got our first snow of the season. The neighborhood looks beautiful covered in 4 inches of snow. / El Miercoles nos cayo la primera nevada y fue una buena, nos cayeron como 10 centimetros de nieve. </p>
<p>
<img alt="" src="https://s3-us-west-2.amazonaws.com/hectorykarla/2014/thanksgiving01_thumb.jpg" />
<img alt="" src="https://s3-us-west-2.amazonaws.com/hectorykarla/2014/thanksgiving02_thumb.jpg" />
<img alt="" src="https://s3-us-west-2.amazonaws.com/hectorykarla/2014/thanksgiving03_thumb.jpg" />
</p>

<p>At night we went to see Eric play at the Tavern. / En la noche nos fuimos a oir tocar a nuestro cuate Eric en un bar en el centro de la ciudad. </p>
<p>
<img alt="" src="https://s3-us-west-2.amazonaws.com/hectorykarla/2014/thanksgiving04_thumb.jpg" />
<img alt="" src="https://s3-us-west-2.amazonaws.com/hectorykarla/2014/thanksgiving05_thumb.jpg" />
<img alt="" src="https://s3-us-west-2.amazonaws.com/hectorykarla/2014/thanksgiving06_thumb.jpg" />
<img alt="" src="https://s3-us-west-2.amazonaws.com/hectorykarla/2014/thanksgiving07_thumb.jpg" />
</p>

<h2 id="cooking">Thanksgiving day</h2>
<p>This year we cooked a rather unconventional meal for Thanksgiving. We cooked "mucbi pollos", a traditional Mayan meal. We have never done this one before and it was quite a challenge but it was fun and tasted delicious! / Para la cena del dia de accion de gracias nos animamos a cocinar un mucbi-pollo que jamas habiamos cocinado y fue toda un aventura prepararlo con base en la receta de mi mama y sus demas consejos. Hice uno de pollo y dos con puerco y la verdad que me quedaron bastante buenos.</p>

<p>Karla was in charge of dessert and she did flan. / Karla estuvo a cargo del postre y se avento un flan.</p>
<p>
<img alt="" src="https://s3-us-west-2.amazonaws.com/hectorykarla/2014/thanksgiving08_thumb.jpg" />
<img alt="" src="https://s3-us-west-2.amazonaws.com/hectorykarla/2014/thanksgiving09_thumb.jpg" />
<img alt="" src="https://s3-us-west-2.amazonaws.com/hectorykarla/2014/thanksgiving10_thumb.jpg" />
</p>

<p>The making of the "mucbi pollos". / Haciendo los mucbi pollos, paso a pasito.</p>
<p>
<img alt="" src="https://s3-us-west-2.amazonaws.com/hectorykarla/2014/thanksgiving11_thumb.jpg" />
<img alt="" src="https://s3-us-west-2.amazonaws.com/hectorykarla/2014/thanksgiving12_thumb.jpg" />
<img alt="" src="https://s3-us-west-2.amazonaws.com/hectorykarla/2014/thanksgiving13_thumb.jpg" />
