<img alt="" src="https://s3-us-west-2.amazonaws.com/hectorykarla/2014/thanksgiving20_thumb.jpg" />
<img alt="" src="https://s3-us-west-2.amazonaws.com/hectorykarla/2014/thanksgiving21_thumb.jpg" />
</p>

<p>Ta-da!!! After an hour and forty five minutes on the oven we get to see if I really nailed it. They were delicious! / Y aqui estan los mucbi pollos saliendo del horno. </p>
<p>
<img alt="" src="https://s3-us-west-2.amazonaws.com/hectorykarla/2014/thanksgiving22_thumb.jpg" />
