<h2>Friday after Thanksgiving day</h2>
<p>We did pretty much nothing today except a short walk with Mac through the neighborhood and had more mucbi pollos for lunch. / El viernes tambien es dia feriado y nos la pasamos en casa descansando y comiendo mas mucbi pollos!</p>
