INSERT INTO blogs VALUES(224,'2015-portland','Portland','2015-02-17 00:55:49.974730','2015-02-18 13:43:34.191281','<p>Early February I attended a week-long conference in Portland. Here are some of the pictures of my trip. / En Febrero atendi una conferencia en Portland, Oregon.</p>


<h2>Sunday</h2>
<p>I got an amazing view of Mount Hood as the plane approached Portland. / De llegada me toco una vista hermosa del Mount Hood, una de las montañas cerca de Portland.</p>
<p><img alt="" src="https://s3-us-west-2.amazonaws.com/hectorykarla/2015/portland01_thumb.jpg" /></p>

<p>As soon as I checked into my hotel, Evan picked me up and we went for lunch to Deschutes Brewery and  walked around town. Here we are trying to move the center ball in this sculpture, we succeeded, if you notice in one of the pictures the little thing sticking out is leaning left and right in the other one. Evan has a much better jumping style than I do. I need to work on that. / Despues de registrarme en el hotel Evan me recogio y nos fuimos a lonchar y pasear por la ciudad. Aqui estamos tratando de mover la pesa que esta al centro de una esculptura y lo logramos, si te fijas el tope de la esculptura esta hacia la derecha en una de las fotos y hacia la izquierda en la otra.</p>
<p>
<img alt="" src="https://s3-us-west-2.amazonaws.com/hectorykarla/2015/portland02_thumb.jpg" />
<img alt="" src="https://s3-us-west-2.amazonaws.com/hectorykarla/2015/portland03_thumb.jpg" />
</p>

<p>After lunch we went to Forrest Park for a short hike. It''s a beautiful area and everything is green even this time of the year. / Despues de lonchar fuimos a un parque que esta cerca de la ciudad. </p>
<p>
<img alt="" src="https://s3-us-west-2.amazonaws.com/hectorykarla/2015/portland04_thumb.jpg" />
<img alt="" src="https://s3-us-west-2.amazonaws.com/hectorykarla/2015/portland05_thumb.jpg" />
<img alt="" src="https://s3-us-west-2.amazonaws.com/hectorykarla/2015/portland06_thumb.jpg" />
<img alt="" src="https://s3-us-west-2.amazonaws.com/hectorykarla/2015/portland07_thumb.jpg" />
<img alt="" src="https://s3-us-west-2.amazonaws.com/hectorykarla/2015/portland08_thumb.jpg" />
</p>

<p>After the hike we went to a different part of town and stopped in a couple of breweries including Cascade Brewing Barrel House and The Big Legrowlski. Abide. / Despues fuimos a un par de bares de los que producen su propia cerveza lo cual es muy tradicional en Portland.</p>
<p>
<img alt="" src="https://s3-us-west-2.amazonaws.com/hectorykarla/2015/portland09_thumb.jpg" />
<img alt="" src="https://s3-us-west-2.amazonaws.com/hectorykarla/2015/portland10_thumb.jpg" />
<img alt="" src="https://s3-us-west-2.amazonaws.com/hectorykarla/2015/portland11_thumb.jpg" />
</p>


<h2>Monday</h2>
<p>Monday the pre-conference started. Here is a peak at the organizers getting ready in the registration area. / La conferencia empezo el lunes, aqui estan los organizadores con los preparativos antes de que lleguen todos a registrarse.</p>
<p><img alt="" src="https://s3-us-west-2.amazonaws.com/hectorykarla/2015/portland12_thumb.jpg" /></p>

<p>For lunch I went to the famous Portland''s food trucks which are quite an experience. One day I tried a Moroccan meal and another an Ethiopian dish. Both were delicious. / Portland es famoso por sus carretones de comida y me toco lonchar en ellos un par de veces, una dia comi un platillo de Moroco y otro uno de Etiopia, ambos estuvieron para chuparse los dedos.</p>
<p>
<img alt="" src="https://s3-us-west-2.amazonaws.com/hectorykarla/2015/portland13_thumb.jpg" />
<img alt="" src="https://s3-us-west-2.amazonaws.com/hectorykarla/2015/portland30_thumb.jpg" />
</p>


<h2>Tuesday</h2>
<p>Tuesday I woke up very early due to the jet lag and went around town to take a few pictures. / Hoy me levante muy muy temprano dado que todavia no me acostumbro al horario y aproveche para irme a tomar unas fotos de la ciudad.</p>
<p>
<img alt="" src="https://s3-us-west-2.amazonaws.com/hectorykarla/2015/portland14_thumb.jpg" />
<img alt="" src="https://s3-us-west-2.amazonaws.com/hectorykarla/2015/portland15_thumb.jpg" />
<img alt="" src="https://s3-us-west-2.amazonaws.com/hectorykarla/2015/portland16_thumb.jpg" />
</p>

<p>Here is a picture of the conference right before the keynote started. / Aqui esta una foto del evento antes de que empiece una de las sesiones plenarias.</p>
<p><img alt="" src="https://s3-us-west-2.amazonaws.com/hectorykarla/2015/portland17_thumb.jpg" /></p>

<p>For dinner me and my team went to Lardo''s. Yummy! After dinner I stopped at Powell City of books and came out with a ton of books. Can you guess which ones are mine and which ones are for Karla? :) / Para cenar me fui con mi equipo a un lugar llamado "Lardo''s" que se traduce algo asi como "Todo de Manteca". De ahi me fui a una libreria muy famosa y sali con media tonelada de libros.</p>
<p>
<img alt="" src="https://s3-us-west-2.amazonaws.com/hectorykarla/2015/portland18_thumb.jpg" />
<img alt="" src="https://s3-us-west-2.amazonaws.com/hectorykarla/2015/portland19_thumb.jpg" />
<img alt="" src="https://s3-us-west-2.amazonaws.com/hectorykarla/2015/portland35_thumb.jpg" />
</p>


<h2>Wednesday</h2>
<p>With jet lag still forcing me to wake very early in the morning, today I walked towards the river and got a nice view of Mount Hood across the bridge as the commuters make their way into town. / Con eso de que todavia no ajusto al cambio de horario hoy me levante muy temprano tambien y me fui rumbo al rio a tomar mas fotos, si te fijas se alcanza a ver el Mount Hood en la foto en que estan los ciclistas cruzando el puente. </p>

<p>
<img alt="" src="https://s3-us-west-2.amazonaws.com/hectorykarla/2015/portland20_thumb.jpg" />
<img alt="" src="https://s3-us-west-2.amazonaws.com/hectorykarla/2015/portland21_thumb.jpg" />
<img alt="" src="https://s3-us-west-2.amazonaws.com/hectorykarla/2015/portland22_thumb.jpg" />
</p>

<p>I gave a lightning talk today on how to understand RDF in comparison to relational databases and Ruby on Rails. You can <a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=G7kgcZh2zeY#t=9110" target="_blank">check out the video here</a>. / Hoy di una corta presentacion (5 minutos) de como se comparan dos de las tecnicas que usamos para representar informacion y <a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=G7kgcZh2zeY#t=9110" target="_blank">la puedes ver en YouTube</a>.</p>

<p>In the afternoon I went back to Cascade Brewing for dinner but this time with my team. / En la noche me fui a cenar con mi equipo un restaurant al otro lado del rio y me toco ver a Mount Hood de nuevo, la foto no le hace justicia, en vivo y a todo color parece que puedes tocar la montaña.</p>
<p>
<img alt="" src="https://s3-us-west-2.amazonaws.com/hectorykarla/2015/portland39_thumb.jpg" />
</p>


<h2>Thursday</h2>
<p>Thursday morning was very foggy. / El jueves por la mañana amanecio muy aneblinado.</p>
<p>
<img alt="" src="https://s3-us-west-2.amazonaws.com/hectorykarla/2015/portland23_thumb.jpg" />
<img alt="" src="https://s3-us-west-2.amazonaws.com/hectorykarla/2015/portland24_thumb.jpg" />
<img alt="" src="https://s3-us-west-2.amazonaws.com/hectorykarla/2015/portland25_thumb.jpg" />
<img alt="" src="https://s3-us-west-2.amazonaws.com/hectorykarla/2015/portland26_thumb.jpg" />
<img alt="" src="https://s3-us-west-2.amazonaws.com/hectorykarla/2015/portland27_thumb.jpg" />
<img alt="" src="https://s3-us-west-2.amazonaws.com/hectorykarla/2015/portland28_thumb.jpg" />
</p>

<p>By the afternoon the fog had cleared and we had beautiful weather with great views of the mountains. These photos are from the 23rd floor of the hotel where one of the sessions took place. I only got a good shot of Mount Hood but I was able to see Mount Rainier and Mount St. Helens as well from here. / Para el medio dia el clima esta divino y nos toco una vista preciosa de la ciudad, estas fotos las tome desde el mirador en el piso 23 del hotel. Solo pude tomar una buena foto de Mount Hood, pero desde aqui me toco ver otras montañas preciosas.</p>
<p>
<img alt="" src="https://s3-us-west-2.amazonaws.com/hectorykarla/2015/portland29_thumb.jpg" />
<img alt="" src="https://s3-us-west-2.amazonaws.com/hectorykarla/2015/portland31_thumb.jpg" />
</p>

<p>At night Evan and I went to the Tugboat Brewing Company in downtown Portland which has a "library" decor. Quite appropriate. / En la noche Evan me llevo a una cerveceria de por aqui, este bar parecia una libreria mas que una bar lo cual fue bastante apropriado dado que mi conferencia fue para programadores y bibliotecarios.</p>
<img alt="" src="https://s3-us-west-2.amazonaws.com/hectorykarla/2015/portland32_thumb.jpg" />


<h2>Friday</h2>
<p>Friday I went to Blue Star doughnuts. Yummy! / Hoy probe las donas de un lugar llamado Blue Star que es famoso por sus donas muy ricas y sofisticadas.</p>
<p>
<img alt="" src="https://s3-us-west-2.amazonaws.com/hectorykarla/2015/portland33_thumb.jpg" />
<img alt="" src="https://s3-us-west-2.amazonaws.com/hectorykarla/2015/portland34_thumb.jpg" />
</p>


<h2>Saturday</h2>
<p>Saturday I woke up very early to start the return trip back home. My connection flight to State College was cancelled and I took a flight to Pittsburgh instead. This is me on my way to the Pittsburgh''s bus station to try to catch a bus to State College, which I did after a 6 hours layover. / El sabado me levante super temprano para empezar el viaje de regreso a casita. Desafortunadamente cancelaron uno de mis vuelos dado a una tormenta en State College asi que tuve que volar a Pittsburgh que esta como a 3 horas de State College. De ahi tome un camion pero tuve que esperar 6 horas antes de la siguiente corrida. Aqui estoy en un taxi en camino a la central.</p>

<p>
<img alt="" src="https://s3-us-west-2.amazonaws.com/hectorykarla/2015/portland36_thumb.jpg" />
</p>

<p>A picture of me once I boarded the Megabus to State College at almost 11 pm. I made it home 3 hours later safe and sound. Karla picked me up and I was very happy to be back home. Home sweet home. / Una foto de mi ya en el camion en camino a State College, estabamos a 14 grados bajo cero centigrados! Llegue a State College a las 2 de la mañana y Karla me fue a recoger. Hogar dulce hogar.</p>
<p>
<img alt="" src="https://s3-us-west-2.amazonaws.com/hectorykarla/2015/portland37_thumb.jpg" />
<img alt="" src="https://s3-us-west-2.amazonaws.com/hectorykarla/2015/portland38_thumb.jpg" />
</p>','https://s3-us-west-2.amazonaws.com/hectorykarla/2015/portland01_thumb.jpg','2015-02-08',2015,NULL,NULL);
