INSERT INTO blogs VALUES(230,'2015-charlottesville','Charlottesville','2015-08-31 01:45:56.843703','2015-08-31 02:35:44.962400','<p>On August 1st we packed both of our cars and drove to Charlottesville. Our furniture was scheduled to arrive within a week so we packed a few essentials to be able to get by. We didn''t do much those days, we basically slept for 10 hours a day and took naps during the day, but we managed to go to MarieBette for breakfast, the downtown mall for drinks, and took a tour of the university grounds. / El primero de agosto manejamos a Charlottesville con ambos carros llenos de los tiliches que sabiamos ibamos a necesitar en la semana que iba a tomar para que nuestros muebles llegaran a casas. No hicimos muchos durante esos dias, la mayor parte del tiempo nos la pasamos durmiendo y descansando, pero si salimos unas cuantas veces a un cafe que esta cerca de la casa, a tomarnos unos tragos al centro y a visitar el campus de la universidad.</p>

