<p>We unpacked our stuff right away when it arrived. But it took us a few weeks to get everything where we wanted, including the art work on the walls. Strange that it''s been only a few weeks, but this place starts to feels like home. Even the grill and the patio furniture are in place. / A pesar de que desempacamos la mayoria de nuestras cosas luego luego, nos llevo un par de semanas poner todo en su lugar y organizado. Es extraño que a pesar de que solo llevamos unas semanas en este lugar, poco a poco la casa y el vecindario se empiezan a sentir a familiares. Hogar dulce hogar. </p>
