INSERT INTO blogs VALUES(232,'2015-nelson-151','Nelson 151','2015-10-12 02:08:52.990734','2015-10-12 03:19:11.432738','<p>On Saturday October 10th, 2015 we drove around Route 151 in Nelson County and had a great time. / El sábado 10 de octubre nos fuimos de paseo a un lugar como a media hora de la casa en la Ruta 151 del condado Nelson. </p>

<h3>Critzer Farm</h3>
<p>We started our tour with a stop at a farm to pick up a couple of pumpkins and then we stayed there also picking up raspberries and blackberries. We got a whole lot more than we should, but we had a lot of fun in the process. / Empezamos nuestro paseo en una granja en la que compramos un par de calabazas por eso de Halloween y ademas cosechamos zarzamoras y frambuesas.</p>

