<h3>Sunday</h3>
<p>On Sunday we figured that we better start eating the raspberries and blackberries that we got yesterday so we had crepes for breakfast and an awesome raspberry tart that Karla prepared. Yummy! / El domingo nos decidimos a empezar a comer las frambuesas y zarzamoras que cosechamos antes de que se nos echen a perder asi que desayunamos crepas y Karla se avento un pie de frambuesas delicioso!</p>

