INSERT INTO blogs VALUES(247,'2016-first-days-in-groton','First Days in Groton','2016-06-27 02:01:40.229941','2016-06-27 02:28:57.515617','<p>On Tuesday May 31st Hector drove from Groton to State College. The next day, Wednesday June 1st, Karla closed on the house. Thursday June 2nd our movers arrived with our furniture and Karla received them. And finally on Friday June 3rd Hector arrived back from State College. It was a marathon of a week but we are happy homeowners again.</p>

